NG0265:13490: swa khya to b+ha ga ba to d+harma bi na ya su pra be di na ta zhes pa /
NG0265:13491: n+ya ya twad a bi ba ri tar+tha tre na d+har+m+ma kle sha ba ni ya zhes te /
NG0265:13492: bcom ldan 'das kyis legs par gsungs pa'i chos 'dul
NG0265:13493: ba gzhan phyi rol dang mi 'dra bar legs par
NG0265:13494: bstan cing go bar byas te rigs pa dang ldan
NG0265:13495: pas na chos / nyon mongs zhi zhing 'dul bar byed pas na 'dus ba ste /
NG0265:13496: tshig bsdus nas bcom ldan 'das kyis legs par gsungs
NG0265:13497: pa'i chos 'du ba legs par bstan pa zhes bya'o
NG0265:13499: nir+ya ni ka sam b+ho d+hi ga ni zhes pa /
NG0265:13500: sam b+ho d+hi ga mi ta+e na nair+yaya ni ka zhes te /
NG0265:13502: 'og mas gong ma bshad pa yin te /
NG0265:13503: rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu 'gro bar byed pas mya
NG0265:13504: ngan las 'das par nges par 'byung ba'i phyir nges
NG0265:13505: par 'byung ba rdzogs pa'i byang chub tu 'gro bar
NG0265:13507: mi mthun med cing 'dus par ldan //
NG0265:13508: a b+hin+na sasdu pa zhes ni /
NG0265:13509: bcom ldan 'das kyi gsung rab la nyan thos rnams blta ba mi mthun pa med de /
NG0265:13510: gcig tu 'dus pas na mi mthun pa med cing 'dus pa dang ldan pa zhes bya'o //
NG0265:13511: brtan pa yod pa sa pra ti sha ra na zhes pas ni bcas pa'am yod pa'o //
NG0265:13512: pra ti sha ra na ni skyabs sam dpung gnyen nam brten du rung ba la bya /
NG0265:13513: mu stegs can gyi chos lta bu khungs ngan par
NG0265:13514: 'byin pa min te rgyal bas gsungs pas brten pa
NG0265:13517: ts+tshan+da blo ti ka zhes pa /
NG0265:13519: blo ti ka ni p+lum ga tau zhes pa ste /
NG0265:13520: 'gro ba'am chus ded cing khyer ba lta bu'i tshig yin te /
NG0265:13521: spyir na 'khor bar skye zhing 'pho ba rgyun bcad pa la bya ste /
NG0265:13522: rgyu ba bcad pa zhes bya'o //
NG0265:13523: chos kyi rnam grangs ma lus mkhyen /
NG0265:13524: bcom ldan 'das kyi chos kyi rnam grangs de rnams
NG0265:13525: mkhyen nas gsungs pa yang theg pa 'og ma pa
NG0265:13526: sngon gyis sbyangs pas mkhyen nas gsung bar 'dod la
NG0265:13527: / gsang sngags la ni bcom ldan 'das thub pa
NG0265:13528: nyid kyang longs sku rigs lnga'i sprul par 'byung bas
NG0265:13530: mngon par shes pa drug dang ldan pas mkhyen //
NG0265:13531: thag ring po dang dus ring po nas gnas shing 'byung ba lkog gyur gyi chos rnams la /
NG0265:13532: da ltar mngon sum du 'dug pa dang 'dra bar shes pa ni mngon par shes pa zhes bya'o //
NG0265:13533: lha yi mig gis mthong ba dang */
NG0265:13534: da ltar gyi lus kyi nye @#/  / ring ji snyed pa dang */
NG0265:13535: shi nas gar skyes pa'i gzugs thams cad mthong ba'o //
NG0265:13536: lha yi rna bas thos pa dang *//
NG0265:13537: sgra skad dang brda sna tshogs thos shing go ba'o //
NG0265:13538: sems kyi rnam grangs shes pa dang *//
NG0265:13539: sems can gyi bsam pa dang bag la nyal che chung shes pa'o //
NG0265:13540: lus kyi rdzu 'phrul shes pa dang */
NG0265:13546: sa la bying ba dag shes pa'o //
NG0265:13547: sngon gyi gnas ni rjes su dran //
NG0265:13548: da ltar gyi dus nas bzung ste tshe snga ma gang gnas /
NG0265:13550: zag pa zad pa mkhyen pa ni //
NG0265:13551: mthong bas spangs pa dang bsgoms pas spangs pa'i nyon mongs pa gang spangs pa dang */
NG0265:13552: ma spangs pa'i rigs shes shing zad pa dang mi skye ba'i ye shes thob pa'o //
NG0265:13553: byang chub sems dpa' nyid du 'dod /
NG0265:13554: byang chub sems dpa' yab yum rnams mngon shes drug dang ldan par gnas pa'o //
NG0265:13555: des sems can ma lus pa la chos 'chad par bskul ma 'debs so //
NG0265:13556: mtshan dang dpe byad ldan gyur pa //
NG0265:13557: mtshan dpe sum cu rtsa gnyis ni //
NG0265:13558: phyag zhabs 'khor lo'i mtshan dang ldan //
NG0265:13559: de bzhin gshegs pa'i phyag dang zhabs kyi mthil la /
NG0265:13560: 'khor lo rtsibs staung dang ldan pa /
NG0265:13561: mu khyud can lte ba dang bcas pa /
NG0265:13562: rnam pa thams cad yongs su rdzogs pa ni 'di lta ste /
NG0265:13563: rus pa'am ba so la brkos pa lta bu mnga' ba ste /
NG0265:13564: de ni bla ma bsu bskyal dang */
NG0265:13565: chos nyan pa la stod pa dang gtsug lag khang
NG0265:13566: dang mchod rten la bsti stang byas pa las byung
NG0265:13567: ba ste / de ni 'khor shin tu mang ba'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13568: zhabs ni shin tu gnas pa dang *//
NG0265:13569: zhabs kyi mthil gnyis mnyam par sa la 'jog cing
NG0265:13570: zhabs zhum pa med pas shin tu gnas pa ni
NG0265:13571: / yi dam la brten pa las byung ba ste /
NG0265:13572: de ni mi g.yo zhing shin tu brtan pa'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13573: phyag zhabs dra bas 'brel pa dang */
NG0265:13574: ngang ba'i rgyal po ltar phyag zhabs kyi sor mo dra bas 'brel ba ni sbyin pa dang *//
NG0265:13577: don mthun pa'i bsdu ba rnam pa bzh-i goms par byas pa las byung ba ste /
NG0265:13578: de ni myur du 'du ba'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13579: phyag zhabs gzhon zhing 'jam pa dang *//
NG0265:13580: bdun yang shin tu mtho ba dang *//
NG0265:13581: phyag dang zhabs shing bal gyi le'u ltar shin tu
NG0265:13582: 'jam zhing gzhon sha chags pa dang phyag zhabs kyi
NG0265:13583: bol bzhi phrag gong gnyis ltag pa dang bdun shin
NG0265:13584: tu mtho ba ni bza' ba dang bca' ba dang
NG0265:13585: */ btung ba zhim zhing nyams su bde ba byin pa las byung ba ste /
NG0265:13586: de gnyis ni bza' ba dang bca' ba dang btung
NG0265:13587: ba shin tu zhim zhing nyams su bde ba thob
NG0265:13589: phyag zhabs sor mo ring ba dang *//
NG0265:13590: bcings pa bkrol ba dang srog gi rim gro byas pa dang */
NG0265:13591: srog gcod pa spangs pas sor mo ring ba dang *//
NG0265:13592: rting pa shin tu yangs pa dang *//
NG0265:13593: rting pa ring bas na rting pa yangs pa dang *//
NG0265:13594: sku yang che zhing drang ba dang *//
NG0265:13595: sku lag pa mdun du 'phags la drang bas sku
NG0265:13596: che zhing drang ba ste de gsum ni sku tshe
NG0265:13598: zhabs ni legs par mtho ba dang *//
NG0265:13599: yan lag spu yang gyen du 'khyil //
NG0265:13600: pus mo'i lha nga dang long bu mdzes pas nub
NG0265:13601: pas zhabs kyi gong mtho ba dang yan lag gi
NG0265:13602: spu gyen du 'khyil ba ni dge ba'i chos yang
NG0265:13603: dag par blangs pa dang bzung ba mngon par spel
NG0265:13604: cing 'grib par ma byas pa yi 'bras bu ste
NG0265:13605: / de ni mi nyams pa'i chos dang ldan pa'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13606: ri dwags e na ya'i byin pa 'dra /
NG0265:13607: smyig ma dang ldum po dang ba b+ha ra drang
NG0265:13608: zhing mnyam la rim gyis gzhol bar grub @#/ /
NG0265:13609: cing byin pa zlum pas ri dwags e na ya'i
NG0265:13610: byin pa lta bu ni rig pa dang bzo'i las
NG0265:13611: rim gror byas shing gzhan la byin pa dang bdag
NG0265:13613: de ni myur du 'dzin pa'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13614: phyag gis brlar ni drang por sleb /
NG0265:13615: brla drang por bzhag ste ma btud kyang phyag gi
NG0265:13616: mthil gnyis kyis pus mo'i lha nga la reg pas
NG0265:13617: phyag brla drang por sleb pa ni bdog cing yod
NG0265:13618: pa'i nor la bslangs na mi 'gong bar gtor zhing
NG0265:13619: med ces ma byas pa'i 'bras bu ste /
NG0265:13620: de ni yo byad la mnga' ba dang */
NG0265:13622: gsang ba'i gnas su sbubs su nub //
NG0265:13623: glang po dang rta cang shes ltar gsang ba'i gnas
NG0265:13624: shin tu mdzes par sbubs su nub pa ni 'grogs
NG0265:13625: pa dang mdza' bshes dang gnyen ma phye ba dang
NG0265:13626: bye bar gyur pa'i sems can rnams la ldum pa
NG0265:13627: dang tshangs spyod la yang dag par bskul ba dang
NG0265:13628: */ gsang ba'i tshig yongs su bsrungs pa las byung ba ste /
NG0265:13629: de ni bu mang ba'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13630: gser zhun lta bu'i mdog dang ldan //
NG0265:13631: mdog kyang shin tu 'jam pa dang *//
NG0265:13632: shin tu sbyangs pa'i gser shin tu sbyangs pa'i kha
NG0265:13633: dog lta bu dang sku la rdul mi 'go bas
NG0265:13634: 'jam zhing snyoms pa'i mdog dang ldan pa ni gdan
NG0265:13635: dang gos dang khang pa dang gzhal med khang dang
NG0265:13636: gnas khang bzang po byin pa las byung ba ste
NG0265:13637: / de gnyis ni gdan dang na bza' dang khang
NG0265:13638: pa dang gzhal med khang dang gnas khang bzang po
NG0265:13640: spu yang re re g.yas phyogs 'khyil //
NG0265:13641: zhal ni mdzod spus brgyan pa dang */
NG0265:13642: shin tu rnam par phye ba'i spu re rer skyes shing gnyis su med pas /
NG0265:13643: spu re re nas g.yas phyogs su 'khyil pa dang */
NG0265:13644: me tog kun+da dang zla ba dang */
NG0265:13645: 'o ma dang ba mo'i mdog ltar 'dug la nyi
NG0265:13646: zla brgya las 'phags par 'od gsal ba'i mdzod spus
NG0265:13647: smin mtshams shin tu brgyan pa ni 'du 'dzi spangs
NG0265:13648: pa dang mkhan slob dang pha ma phu nu la
NG0265:13649: sogs pa bla ma rnams la tshul dang 'dra bar
NG0265:13651: bsgo ba rna lam gzan pa las byung ba ste /
NG0265:13652: de ni mnyam pa med pa'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13653: seng+ge'i ro stod lta bu la //
NG0265:13654: phrag pa'i lhun ni mdzes par grub //
NG0265:13655: ro stod che bas seng+ge'i ro stod dang */
NG0265:13656: mgul dang rgyud legs par 'brel cing lhun zlum pas phrag pa'i lhun mdzes par grub pa ste /
NG0265:13657: de ni mi snyan pa mi zer zhing mi spyo la mi smod pa las /
NG0265:13658: snyan par smra zhing legs par bshad pa mthun par 'dzin pa las byung ba ste /
NG0265:13659: de ni thub pa med pa'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13660: phrag so bzhin du rgyas pa dang *//
NG0265:13661: ro yang thams cad bro ba'i mchog / gser gyi
NG0265:13662: gtan pa shin tu phyis pa ltar phrag so legs
NG0265:13664: rlung mkhris bad kan gyis ma nyams shing rnam par
NG0265:13665: shes pa'i 'dra ba med pas ro bro ba'i mchog
NG0265:13666: dang ldan pa de dag ni nad pa rnams la
NG0265:13667: rtsi dang rim gro dang sman dang nyams su phan
NG0265:13668: pa'i zas byin pa dang rim gro byas pa las
NG0265:13669: byung ba ste / de gnyis ni nad nyung ba'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13670: n+ya gro d+ha ltar chu zheng 'gab //
NG0265:13671: dbu yi spyi gtsug g.yas ldan 'khyil //
NG0265:13672: sku chu zheng 'dom du mnyam pas shing n+ya gro d+ha ltar chu shing 'gab pa dang */
NG0265:13673: spyi gtsug zlum zhing legs la g.yas phyogs su 'khyil
NG0265:13674: ba dang ldan pa'i dbu mnyam zhing legs par grub
NG0265:13675: la mdzes pa mnga' bas dbu spyi gtsug dang ldan
NG0265:13679: rdzing bu dang brgal dka' ba'i zam pa dang */
NG0265:13680: kha zas 'greng ba'i gnas dang stegs dang gtsug lag
NG0265:13681: khang bya ba la sogs pa gzhan mos par bya
NG0265:13682: ba sngon du btang zhing bdag gis gzhan la byin
NG0265:13684: de ni mnga' ba chen po mnga'
NG0265:13687: yangs shing srab pa'i ljags dang ni //
NG0265:13688: gsung ni tshangs pa'i dbyangs dang ldan //
NG0265:13689: ljags ut+pal la dmar po'i kha dog ltar 'dug cing
NG0265:13690: shin tu yangs shing srab pa dang tshangs pa'i dbyangs
NG0265:13691: dang bya ka la ping ka lta bu'i gsung mnga'
NG0265:13692: ba ste / de dag ni yun ring por tshig
NG0265:13693: snyan cing 'jam pa dang nyams su bde ba smras
NG0265:13695: de gnyis ni yan lag lnga dang ldan pa'i gsung mnga' ba'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13696: gsung yan lag lnga dang ldan pa ni yongs su
NG0265:13697: shes shing rnam par shes par 'gyur ba dang mnyan
NG0265:13698: na dga' zhing mi mthun pa med pa dang */
NG0265:13699: zab cing dbyangs rjes su 'byung ba dang */
NG0265:13700: gtad mi bra zhing rnar snyan pa dang */
NG0265:13703: 'gram pa me long gi dkyil ltar legs par grub
NG0265:13704: cing mdzes par skyes te yid du 'ong bas yun
NG0265:13705: ring po nas tshig 'khyal pa spangs shing dus su
NG0265:13706: smra bas seng+ge'i 'gram pa lta bu ste /
NG0265:13707: de ni tshig kun gyis mnyan pa'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13708: tshems ni shin tu dkar ba dang *//
NG0265:13709: tshems kyang shin tu mnyam pa dang *//
NG0265:13710: me tog kun+da dang dung gis bcag 'phro ltar shin tu dka' ba'i tshims mnga' ba dang */
NG0265:13711: tshems la mtho dman med pas mnyam pa ni rim gro bya ba dang */
NG0265:13712: brnyas pa med pa gnyis kyi 'tsho ba yongs su dag pa las byung ba ste /
NG0265:13713: de gnyis ni 'khor snga nas bsags pa'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13714: tshems kyi thags kyang bzang ba dang *//
NG0265:13715: tshems mnyam zhing grangs bla 'og dgye dgu med par bzhi bcu tshang ba dang */
NG0265:13716: tshems la mtshams ma dod pas thags bzang ba dang */
NG0265:13717: bla 'og dgye dgu med pas mnyam zhing bzhi bcu tshang ba ni /
NG0265:13718: yun ring po nas bden zhing phra ma med pa'i tshig smra ba las byung ba ste /
NG0265:13719: de dag ni 'khor dbyer mi phyed pa'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13720: spyan yang dkar nag 'byes pa dang *//
NG0265:13721: ba yi rdzi ma lta bu'o //
NG0265:13722: spyan dkar nag gi cha ma 'dres shing shin tu
NG0265:13723: rnam par dag cing mdog dmar pos ma g.yogs pas
NG0265:13725: rdzi ma bla 'og shin tu legs par gnas la
NG0265:13726: ma 'dzings pas ba'i rdzi ma lta bu ni pang
NG0265:13727: gis 'khyud pa bzhin du nyes par bsam pa med
NG0265:13728: la ma chags mi sdang ba dang */
NG0265:13729: rmongs pa med pa'i mig gis bltas pa las 'byung ba ste /
NG0265:13730: de dag ni kun nas mdzes pa'i snga ltas so //
NG0265:13731: de rnams ni de bzhin gshegs pa'i mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis so //
NG0265:13732: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cu ni //
NG0265:13733: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni mngon par 'du bya ba thams cad las dben pa ste //
NG0265:13734: sen mo zangs kyi mdog ltar 'dug / sangs rgyas
NG0265:13735: bcom ldan 'das rnams ni zhe sa thams cad kyi
NG0265:13736: 'go la sbyar ba'i gnyen bshes byams pa dang 'dra
NG0265:13737: bar sems can thams cad la phan pa dang bde
NG0265:13739: sen mo'i mdog kyang snum pa yin //
NG0265:13740: rigs rgyud mthon por byung ba ste //
NG0265:13741: sen mo mtho ba yin zhing tshul kha na ma tho ba mi mnga' bas sen mo zlum /
NG0265:13743: dge ba'i rtsa ba shin tu 'tshogs pa ste //
NG0265:13744: sor mo rgyas la dge rtsa rim gyis grub pa ste sor mo /
NG0265:13747: sku gsung thugs kyi phrin las dang 'tsho ba shin tu dben pa ste sku'i /
NG0265:13748: rtsa yang mi mngon pa yin /
NG0265:13749: nyon mongs pa'i mdud bgrol bas rtsa la mdud pa med /
NG0265:13751: shin tu dben pa'i chos mnga' bas //
NG0265:13752: long bu mi mngon pa yin /
NG0265:13753: mi mnyam pa thams cad las sgrol bas zhabs kyang mnyam /
NG0265:13756: seng ge'i stabs su bzhud pa yin /
NG0265:13757: mi'i glang po ste glang po'i @#//
NG0265:13760: ngang pa'i rgyal po ltar nam mkha' la bzhud pa ste //
NG0265:13761: ngang pa'i stabs su bzhud pa yin /
NG0265:13762: khyu mchog ste khyu mchog gi stabs /
NG0265:13764: mthun pa'i lam mnga' ba ste //
NG0265:13765: g.yas phyogs su bzhud cing blta na mdzes pa ste /
NG0265:13768: rtag tu thugs yon po mi mnga' ste //
NG0265:13769: mi yo bar bzhud pa yin /
NG0265:13770: tshul rnam par dag pa'i yon tan ston pas sku yang legs /
NG0265:13772: sdig pa'i chos rnams shin tu sbyangs pa ste sku shin tu sbyangs pa yin /
NG0265:13773: chos rim gyis ston pas sku rim gyis gzhol /
NG0265:13775: sku gsung thugs gtsang ba dang ldan pas na //
NG0265:13777: rang bzhin gyis thugs 'jam pa dang ldan pas sku shin tu 'jam pa yin /
NG0265:13778: rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa'i thugs mnga' bas
NG0265:13779: sku shin tu rnam par dag pa yin / !
NG0265:13780: chos dang 'dul ba shin tu rdzogs pa dang ldan
NG0265:13781: pas // dpe byad shin tu rdzogs pa yin la
NG0265:13782: yon tan yangs shing bzang bsten pa ste sku che
NG0265:13784: sems can thams cad la mnyam pa'i thugs mnga' ste sku //
NG0265:13786: mchog tu 'jam pa'i chos ston pas te sku /
NG0265:13789: rtag tu zhum pa med pa'i thugs mnga' ba ste sku //
NG0265:13791: mi dge ba'i rtsa ba thams cad byang ba ste sku shin tu /
NG0265:13792: rgyas shing yang 'byung ba shin tu bcom zhing zad pa ste sku shin tu mkhregs /
NG0265:13794: rten cing 'brel 'byung gi yan lag dang nying lag legs par ston pa ste //
NG0265:13795: yan lag nying lag spa bar mdzes /
NG0265:13797: gzigs pa shin tu rnam par dag pa ste //
NG0265:13798: snang ba rab rib med cing rnam par dag pa yin /
NG0265:13799: tshul dang ldan pa'i slob ma mnga' ba ste //
NG0265:13801: 'khor ba'i nyes pa thams cad shin tu sbyangs pa ste phyal shin tu /
NG0265:13802: byang ba dang ldan pa yin /
NG0265:13803: nga rgyal ba'i de'u bcom pa ste phyal /
NG0265:13805: chos zad pa rnam par bzlog pas phyal phyam /
NG0265:13807: chos zab mo thugs su chud pa ste //
NG0265:13809: mthun par 'dzin pa'i slob ma mnga' ba ste lte ba g.yas phyogs su 'khyil /
NG0265:13811: slob ma kun nas mdzes pa'i dge 'dun mnga' ba ste //
NG0265:13813: thugs shin tu gtsang ba dang ldan pa ste kun spyod shin tu gtsang ba yin /
NG0265:13814: chos nag po bstan pa dang bral ba'i chos dang 'dul ba la mnga' ba ste /
NG0265:13817: shing bal ltar yang ba rab tu thob pa'i chos ston pas //
NG0265:13818: phyag shing bal ltar 'jam pa yin /
NG0265:13819: rang gi skye bo dang skye bo phal pa la
NG0265:13820: byams pas dge sbyong chen po brnyes pa ste phyag
NG0265:13821: gi ri mo snum pa yin la shin tu zab
NG0265:13822: cing brtan par bzhugs pas phyag gi ri mo zab
NG0265:13824: bzod pa'i chos yangs pa ston pa ste phyag gi ri mo //
NG0265:13825: ring ba yin la bslab pa'i gnas ha cang yang mi ring bar 'cha' bas zhal /
NG0265:13826: ha cang mi ring ba yin la /
NG0265:13827: gzugs brnyan 'jig rten thams cad du bkye ba ste //
NG0265:13828: zhal la gzugs kyi gzugs brnyan snang ba yin //
NG0265:13829: yon tan ba'i tshogs dang ldan pas te //
NG0265:13831: 'jam pa sngon du gtang zhing 'dul bas ljags 'jam pa yin /
NG0265:13832: byams pa'i skye bo 'dod chags pa rnams kyi chos
NG0265:13833: dang 'dul ba gting dpag dka' bas ljags shin tu
NG0265:13834: dmar ba yin // glang po'i sgra dang 'brug gi sgra dbyangs ltar ba bsnyengs pa mi mnga' bas //
NG0265:13835: glang po'i nga ro dang 'brug gi dbyangs /
NG0265:13837: snyan cing 'jam pa dang nyams su @#//
NG0265:13838: bde bar smra ba'i slob ma mnga' bas //
NG0265:13839: snyan cing 'jam pa nyams su bde ba'i gsung dang ldan pas /
NG0265:13840: srid pa kun tu sbyor ba las 'das pas //
NG0265:13841: tshems mche ba shin tu zlum pa yin /
NG0265:13842: skye bo rno ba rnams 'dul bas tshems mche ba /
NG0265:13844: chos dang 'dul ba shin tu dkar bas tshems mche ba /
NG0265:13846: sa'i phyogs mnyam pa la bzhugs pa ste mche ba /
NG0265:13848: rim gyis mngon par rtogs pa'i chos ston pas tshems mche ba /
NG0265:13850: shes rab kyi ri mthon po la bzhugs pas //
NG0265:13851: shangs legs par mtho ba dang ldan pa yin /
NG0265:13852: 'dul ba'i skye bo gtsang ma mnga' bas shangs shin tu gtsang ba dang */
NG0265:13853: sangs rgyas kyis chos phul du yangs pa mnga' ba //
NG0265:13855: gzigs pa shin tu rnam par dag pa spyan /
NG0265:13857: sems can gyi tshogs shin tu bsags pa ste /
NG0265:13859: lha dang mi dang lha ma yin dang skye bu
NG0265:13860: dang na chung mchog mig dkar nag 'byes shing pad+ma'i
NG0265:13861: 'dab ltar 'dug pa rnams kyis mngon par dga' bar
NG0265:13865: rtag tu yangs pa gzigs pa ste //
NG0265:13866: smin ma ring ba dang ldan pa yin /
NG0265:13867: 'jam par 'dul ba la mkhas pas smin ma 'jam pa yin /
NG0265:13868: skyon thams cad mkhyen pa ste smin ma'i spu mnyam pa dang ldan pa yin /
NG0265:13869: dag pa'i rtsa ba'i snum gyis sems snum par gyur pa'i skye bo 'dul ba ste smin ma snum /
NG0265:13871: chos mchog tu yangs shing don dang ldan pas //
NG0265:13872: snyan legs shing snyan shal ring ba yin //
NG0265:13873: nyon mongs pa'i rgyud las rnam par rgyal bas //
NG0265:13875: sems can bsam pa nyams pa 'dul ba ste snyan gyi /
NG0265:13876: dbang po mnyam pa dang ldan no //
NG0265:13877: lta ba'i rnam pa thams cad yongs su byang bas //
NG0265:13878: zhal 'phral ba legs par grub pa yin /
NG0265:13879: phas kyis rgol ba 'dul ba ste zhal /
NG0265:13882: smon lam dam pa shin tu rdzogs pas //
NG0265:13883: dbu shin tu rgyas pa yin /
NG0265:13884: yul gyi bung ba rnam par bzlog pa ste dbu
NG0265:13885: bung ba ltar gnag cing mthong ba dang bsgoms pas
NG0265:13886: spangs pa'i bag la nyal zad par byed pas dbu
NG0265:13889: thugs 'jam pas bstan pa'i snying po thugs su chud pas dbu //
NG0265:13890: 'jam zhing rtag tu ma 'khrugs pa'i thugs dang ldan
NG0265:13891: pas dbu mi 'dzings brlang po'i gsung dang yongs su
NG0265:13892: bral bas dbu mi rtsub la /
NG0265:13894: byang chub kyi yan lag spos kyi me tog gis skye bo mthun par bsgrub pas //
NG0265:13895: dbu yi dri ni zhim pa yin //
NG0265:13896: sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das rnams ni //
NG0265:13897: phyag dang zhabs dpal be'u dang bkra shis dang dga' ba 'khyil /
NG0265:13899: de nas sangs rgyas rnams kyis phrin las cho 'phrul chen por bstan pa 'di dag gsungs so //
NG0265:13900: cho 'phrul rnam pa gsum nyid de //
NG0265:13901: kun brjod pa yi cho 'phrul dang *//
NG0265:13903: rjes su bstan pa'i cho 'phrul yin //
NG0265:13904: phrin las rnam pa bzhi nyid de //
NG0265:13905: gnod pa nad sogs zhi ba dang *//
NG0265:13906: tshe ring longs spyod rgyas pa dang *//
NG0265:13907: pha rol dbang du bya ba dang *//
NG0265:13908: drag shul spyod pa bya ba'o //
NG0265:13909: de nas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dbugs dbyung ba'i
NG0265:13910: dkyil 'khor chen po drug tu sgom pa 'di gsungs
NG0265:13912: rdo rje sems dpa' zhal gsum @#//
NG0265:13913: dbus mthing g.yas dkar g.yon dmar /
NG0265:13914: phyag drug gi dang po gnyis na //
NG0265:13915: rdor dril g.yas 'bar thod pa mchan khung na kha tam ga / g.yon bar na /
NG0265:13916: ral gri g.yas tha ma na cang te'u g.yon tha ma na mgo bo 'chang */
NG0265:13917: yum / phag mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yon thod pa g.yas gri gug sku mdog dmar /
NG0265:13920: rnam snang dang yum gshin rje gshed mo yab yum gnyis ka sku mdog ser /
NG0265:13923: rdo rje nyi ma dang yum skrag byed ma sku mdog ser po dmar /
NG0265:13925: pad+ma gar dbang dang yum rmongs byed ma gnyis dmar /
NG0265:13927: yab / rta mchog rgyal po rdo rje dang yum gtum mo gnyis ka ljang gu 'o yin /
NG0265:13928: yab khrag 'thung dang yum skyod byed ma gnyis sku mdog sngon por gnas /
NG0265:13930: dpa' bo zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa //
NG0265:13932: thod pa dang ni g.yas dang po na kha tam ga / g.yon dngapo na /
NG0265:13933: rang mtshan dril bu g.yas tha ma na cang te'u bsnams //
NG0265:13934: dpa' mo yum lnga po zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas gri gug g.yon thod /
NG0265:13947: rdo rje rgyal po rta mchog don grub /
NG0265:13960: om badzra ha badzra sa twa yab rdo rje sems dpa' hu~m hu~m phat swaha /
NG0265:13961: a+om bam badzra bam ti yum phag mo hu~m hu~m phat swa ha /
NG0265:13962: a+om hi badzra bai ro tsa na rnam snang hu~m hu~m phat swa ha /
NG0265:13964: gshin rje ma ya ma ni hu~m hu~m phat swaha /
NG0265:13965: om swa ha hu~m pad+ma gar dbang pad+ma nirti shwa ra hu~m hu~m phat swa ha /
NG0265:13966: a+om hrim mam mo ha ni rmongs byed ma hu~m hu~m phat swaha /
NG0265:13967: a+om bam shad he he ru ka khrag 'thung hu~m hu~m phat swa ha /
NG0265:13968: om hrim hrim sam tsa la ni skyod byed ma hu~m hu~m phat swaha /
NG0265:13969: om hu~m hu~m ho badzra sur+ya rdo rje nyi ma hu~m hu~m phat swa ha /
NG0265:13970: om hu~m hu~m sam skrag byed ma trar+sha sa ni hu~m hu~m phat swa ha /
NG0265:13971: om pad ham pad d+ham pa ra ma sha rdo rje rgyal po rta mchog hu~m hu~m phat swaha /
NG0265:13972: om phat phat tsan+ti gtum mo ka hu~m hu~m phat swaha /
NG0265:13974: tshor ba rdo rje nyi ma /
NG0265:13976: 'du byed rta mchog / rnam shes rdo rje sems
NG0265:13977: dpa' de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag nyid
NG0265:13979: phung po lnga dang thams cad kun //
NG0265:13980: dpa' bo drug la yang dag gnas //
NG0265:13981: mig gnyis gti mug rdo rje la mi ni /
NG0265:13982: rna ba zhe sdang rdo rje phag mo /
NG0265:13983: sna ser sna rdo rje skrag byed ma /
NG0265:13984: kha 'dod chags rdo rje rmongs byed ma /
NG0265:13985: reg bya phrag dog rdo rje gtum mo /
NG0265:13986: skye mched thams cad dbang phyug rdo rje bskyod byed ma'o //
NG0265:13987: dbang po dpa' mor gnas pa yin //
NG0265:13988: lus rnam snang rdo rje dang ngag dpag med rdo
NG0265:13989: rje yid mi 'khrugs pa zhes so rdo rjer gnas
NG0265:13990: // de nas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor bsgrub par bya ba 'di gsungs so //
NG0265:13991: zhi ba'i lha tshogs mchod pas mnyes par bya ba dag ni //
NG0265:13992: yan lag mchod pa'i las la mkhas pas dbul bar bya /
NG0265:13995: dmigs pa med pa'i dpe ni mkha' ltar dag pas 'khor 'das kun la khyab pa'i sku /
NG0265:13996: 'das pa'i thugs dang sems can gyi sems dbyer med pa'i chos sku las /
NG0265:13998: spyan 'dren pa dang ye shes kyi lha gshegs su @#//
NG0265:13999: gsol bar gnyis su mi dmigs kyang */
NG0265:14001: thugs rje'i ma 'gags pa ngang nyid chos sku dag pa las /
NG0265:14003: ye shes sgyu mas 'i sku snang la rang bzhin med pa rol cing chu zla ltar /
NG0265:14006: thugs rje tshad med pa'i lcags kyus rta mthur ltar bzung nas thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul zhing *//
NG0265:14007: byams pa'i tshad med pa zhags pas rta mthur mdas
NG0265:14008: bkris pa ltar mi gtong bas gnas nas spyan yang
NG0265:14009: 'dren // dga' ba'i tshad med pa lcags sgrog pho
NG0265:14010: nyas rta mthur dam du bsdom pa ltar bsdams nas
NG0265:14011: 'dren // gnas stobs la // btang snyoms tshad med
NG0265:14012: pa'i dril bus rnam grol rgyal po rta zhon pa
NG0265:14013: la dga' gtam zer ba ltar dgyes pa bskyed /
NG0265:14016: rang snang ba dang dbyer med pas na dkyil 'khor la //
NG0265:14017: thugs rjes ma 'gags pa rgya mtsho'i rlabs 'dra ba las mgon gyur ma lus rnams /
NG0265:14018: chos nyid dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i ngang du dgongs la //
NG0265:14019: mi phyed dbyings la 'god mdzad pa'i //
NG0265:14020: bdag rnal 'byor pa la dam tshig gis dgongs pa lus ngag yid la dgyes shing thim par bzhugs //
NG0265:14021: rgyal ba'i sangs rgyas kyi sku la bzhengs pa dang bzhugs pa mi mnga' yang *//
NG0265:14022: ye shes ngang du ye shes lha dang bdag dang
NG0265:14023: chos nyid rnams dbyer med par rgyud gcig pa yin
NG0265:14024: pas na / mi gnyis gcig pas na //
NG0265:14025: thabs yab dang rang bzhin med pa'i shes rab yum ma 'gags pa'i ting 'dzin dkyil 'khor 'dir /
NG0265:14027: mi g.yo bar dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol /
NG0265:14029: dbyings kun rang bzhin 'khor ba'i chos kyi nyes skyon rnam par dag pa las /
NG0265:14030: ma 'gags pas sems can gyi don la /
NG0265:14031: thugs rje'i dbang gis sprul pa'i skur bzhengs pa //
NG0265:14032: rdo rje dbyings kyi lha tshogs bzhi bcu gnyis //
NG0265:14033: su snang ba de yang glo bur du byas pa ni ma yin no //
NG0265:14035: rang snang gi lha tshogs mang po rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0265:14036: bde bar gshegs so gdul bya'i yul las sangs rgyas /
NG0265:14038: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i ye shes kyis //
NG0265:14039: srid pa rgya mtsho dbul byi'i rdzas mtha' yas kun //
NG0265:14041: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol /
NG0265:14042: phyi ltar dri chab nang bdud rtsi /
NG0265:14044: srid pa'i rtsa ba chos kyi dbyings su shar ba'i phyir ma 'gags par mchod rdzas te /
NG0265:14046: de nyid ma bcos pa'i ngang las gsal ba ltar /
NG0265:14047: yum gyi thig ler pad+ma rak+sha ltar shar //
NG0265:14048: chags yul bde ba'i 'od phung nang ltar thugs rje chags pa'i rtags su rak+ta /
NG0265:14051: nyon mongs pa rnams chos kyi dbyings su bstim phyir
NG0265:14052: phyi bdud rtsi'i nang rak+ta gsang ba byang sems ar+g+ham
NG0265:14054: 'byung ba yum lnga nyid kyi ngang las dbyings nas ye shes bcud shar ba /
NG0265:14055: ni gsang ba rnam shes tshogs brgyad ye shes su gsal lo //
NG0265:14056: snang srid kyi mdangs ldan rang rig pa'i me tog
NG0265:14057: ni rang sems mi rtog pa ste nang rang rig
NG0265:14059: gnyis su med pa'i ngang las ma 'gag pa'i phyi me tog kha dog cir yang gsal /
NG0265:14061: me tog / 'bras bu'i bcud dang ldan @#//
NG0265:14062: me tog kha dog 'od phung dang ldan par 'bul /
NG0265:14064: ma bcos pa'i ngang las ma 'gags par shar ba'i rang byung dam rdzas spos mchog 'di /
NG0265:14065: dud pa'i kha dog chos dbyings nam mkha' gsal dris sna'i dbang po tshims par byed pa //
NG0265:14066: stong gsum dri bsung nang ltar gsur chen gyi dud pas /
NG0265:14067: gsang ba byang sems bdud rtsi'i dris /
NG0265:14070: 'bar ba'i lha'i shangs la mchod pas mnyes gyur cig
NG0265:14071: / snod yum bcud yab gnyis med yab yum dag
NG0265:14072: pa la / yab kyi khu ba gsang ba'i mar me /
NG0265:14073: nang ltar rang byung ye shes kyi rtags su //
NG0265:14074: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes me shar nas /
NG0265:14075: kong bu dur khrod gzhal yas khang mar khu tshil chen me ye shes kyi rang bzhin no //
NG0265:14076: mtha' dbus med par gsal ba'i 'od 'bar ni /
NG0265:14077: phyi kong bu stong gsum rtsi mar rgya mtsho tsam me stong gsum /
NG0265:14079: 'khor ba'i ma rig pa'i mun khang sra ba gzhom phyir bzhes su gsol /
NG0265:14080: gsang ba ltar yab yum gnyis su dri chab khu ba dkar dmar //
NG0265:14081: gnyis med mkha' dbyings dag pa'i pho brang du /
NG0265:14083: nyon mongs pa lha mor dag pas skyon bral dag
NG0265:14084: pa lha mo mang po tsan+dan gyi 'de gus byug
NG0265:14086: phyi ltar tsan+dan la sogs pa'i dri //
NG0265:14087: cir yang 'char phyir dri yi 'od dpung 'bul //
NG0265:14088: zhal gyi dbyings su thim ro phro ba'i mchog yin
NG0265:14089: pas na dgos pa la sku nyams su brtas pa'o
NG0265:14090: / nas mnyes gyur cig / gnas gang nas byung na //
NG0265:14091: nam mkha' kun bzang dbyings nas cir yang 'byung */
NG0265:14092: gsang ba byang sems yid bzhin nor bu rin che //
NG0265:14094: 'byung ba'i 'bras bu nang ltar 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga /
NG0265:14095: phyi ltar zhal zas ro mchog brgya ldan gyi //
NG0265:14096: lha bshos rin chen yid bzhin longs spyod 'di /
NG0265:14098: sku nang 'dod yon gsung gsang ba byang sems thugs kyi ngang du thim par bsam /
NG0265:14099: dang po rna ba'i yul du /
NG0265:14100: sgra yi dngos por snang ba yang */
NG0265:14101: sgra'i dngos po rdos bcas su //
NG0265:14102: yod pa ma yin rna bar shin tu grags //
NG0265:14103: sgra yis phy-i sgra snyan gyis yid rab tu tshim gyur kyang *//
NG0265:14104: sgra nyid rang bzhin gang yang med /
NG0265:14105: nang ltar sgra rang bzhin med par rtogs so //
NG0265:14106: sgra 'byung gsang ba chos thams cad la sgra brnyan ltar shes pas rang bzhin mchod par 'bul /
NG0265:14108: sku nang gsung gsang ba thugs kyi dngos grub stsol /
NG0265:14109: bdud rtsi lnga rang gi lus las byung bas na //
NG0265:14110: rang byung de yang ye gdod ma nas dag pa'i rdzas //
NG0265:14111: bdud rtsi lnga re re las spas pa nang gi bzhi //
NG0265:14112: rtsa mngon pa phyi'i bzhi ste brgyad /
NG0265:14113: brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NG0265:14114: yan lag phyi'i ming gi yin pas na yan lag stong gi sman //
NG0265:14115: ra sa ya na la sogs rdzas //
NG0265:14116: rigs lnga dri chen rnam snang byang sems rdo rje
NG0265:14117: sha chen rin 'byung rak+ta mtha' yas dri chu don
NG0265:14118: grub / dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NG0265:14119: ye shes lnga rdzogs dri chen chos dbyings byang sems me long */
NG0265:14120: sha mnyam nyid rak+ta kun rtog / dri chu bya ba grub pa /
NG0265:14126: dri chus lha min dang yi dwags /
NG0265:14128: dug lnga sel dri chen gti mug sel de bzhin sbyar ba'i bdud rtsi 'di /
NG0265:14131: bcom ldan rig lnga yab yum dang */
NG0265:14132: phul bas phung po dang 'byung ba lnga dag par mdzad //
NG0265:14133: byang chub sems dpa' lcam dral dang *//
NG0265:14134: rnams la phul ba rang rgyud dag par mdzad //
NG0265:14135: kun bzang yab yid dang yum chos dag thub drug dang */
NG0265:14136: nyon mongs drug / sgo skyong yab yum lus kyi khams dag mtha' bzhi las grol /
NG0265:14137: mkha' 'gro sangs rgyas bstan pa dang 'khor bcas la /
NG0265:14139: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul /
NG0265:14141: thugs rjes bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NG0265:14142: dngos grub gang thob na dam tshig nyams pa rnams //
NG0265:14143: tshangs pa nas 'phrul dang 'dra ba'i gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0265:14144: lce yi dam dngos grub len pa'i dam tshig lce rdo rjer bsam /
NG0265:14146: rdo rje khong seng can gyi nang du 'dren pa'i hu~m bsgoms te /
NG0265:14148: mthe bong dang ni shes rab srin lag rtses //
NG0265:14149: thabs yab zla dkyil dang shes rab yum nyi dkyil 'brel ba yis /
NG0265:14152: bdud rtsi rnam lnga sbyar ba la /
NG0265:14153: lce la ro mchog tshor ba //
NG0265:14154: myangs na sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rdo rje gsum 'thob 'gyur /
NG0265:14156: dri ma med cing rnam par dag pa'i dpe nam mkha'i rang bzhin las /
NG0265:14158: log rtog mtshan ma mang po sprin phung bzhin /
NG0265:14159: sprin rlung gis gtor ba'i dpes //
NG0265:14160: ye shes nyi zer 'od kyis rab sprin dang bral
NG0265:14161: ba'i nyi ma shar ba ltar log rtog dag pa'i
NG0265:14164: dag pa'i don du gsang nan 'bul lo rtogs nas mchod par bgyi /
NG0265:14166: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang */
NG0265:14168: 'dod pa'i yon tan gyi lha mo rnam pa lnga //
NG0265:14169: chos nyid skye ba med dbyings las /
NG0265:14171: rang gang 'dod pa'i gsol ba btab cing phul bas //
NG0265:14172: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin grub 'bul //
NG0265:14173: bzang ngan che chung med pas //
NG0265:14174: mnyam nyid rtog pa'i rlung gis /
NG0265:14175: mi g.yo bzang ngan che chung med pas //
NG0265:14176: mnyam nyid mchog gi chos nyid yon tan can /
NG0265:14178: thugs rje'i bdag nyid 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal thams cad sel bar mdzad /
NG0265:14180: yon tan mtha' yas pa dang ldan pas gdul bya la dngos grub thams cad sbyin mdzad pa /
NG0265:14182: dri ma med cing chos nyid las mi g.yo bar
NG0265:14183: 'gro ba so sor mi 'byed pas mnyam med dam
NG0265:14184: pa'i dngos grub mchog chos can /
NG0265:14187: yon tan shin tu brtag dka' bas na phra ba'i cha la yang tshad gzung du med de //
NG0265:14188: dpe ni nam mkha' mtha' yas pa ltar dang yang
NG0265:14189: yon tan mtha' yas pa 'gran du mnyam pa yod
NG0265:14190: ma yin / mchog thun mong gi / dngos grub
NG0265:14191: rnam gnyis gzhan dang mnyam pa med dpe yid bzhin
NG0265:14192: nor bu dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i dpe bas lhag pa'o
NG0265:14193: ma yin / / dang bral ba rnams /
NG0265:14194: dngos grub de gang la sbyin na //
NG0265:14195: sems can khams las can la mchog gi dngos grub
NG0265:14196: mchog rnams sems nyid chos skur gsal bar ston nges
NG0265:14198: rtag tu gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma med pa'i phyir mi dmigs pa las thugs rje'i shugs las byung */
NG0265:14199: ba ni nyi ma shar bas sems can la @#//
NG0265:14201: smon lam gang btab pa de grub pa ste thugs
NG0265:14202: la gang yang 'gag pa med pa'i nam mkha'i chos
NG0265:14203: nyid can / cir yang snang ba'i yon tan gang yang ma 'gags par 'char ba'o //
NG0265:14204: 'gro ba'i don mngon mtho nges legs grub rab tu brtson pa ni mtha' yas pa /
NG0265:14207: thugs rje chen po'i bdag nyid dus rtag tu nam
NG0265:14208: mkha' ltar 'gyur ba med par dus rtag tu bzhugs
NG0265:14209: rnam par snang */ 'jig rten na yon tan /
NG0265:14210: tshad med pas tshad gzung ba dang bral ba chos nyid shin tu yongs su rdzogs pa'i /
NG0265:14211: rnam rtog gi zug rngu dang bral nas //
NG0265:14212: bde bar chos skur gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa'i go 'phang dam pa brnyes gyur kyang */
NG0265:14213: pas gdul bya'i don mdzad bya mdzad byed kyi rtogs pa mi mnga' /
NG0265:14214: 'dod khams gzugs khams gzugs med khams gsum rnams la
NG0265:14215: phyag rgya chen po mchog gi dngos grub mchog stsol
NG0265:14216: zhing ster bar mdzad de rang sems chos sku dri
NG0265:14217: med du gnas pa'i don rtogs par /
NG0265:14219: thugs rje'i chen pos sems can gyis don mdzad pa spyod pa mi g.yo 'gag par yongs mi 'gyur //
NG0265:14220: zhing mi 'gag ste yid bzhin gyi nor bu ltar 'gro don 'gag med du mdzad do //
NG0265:14221: e ma ho ni ngam zhing mtshor pa'o //
NG0265:14222: so sor rtogs pa'i ye shes kyis chos spyi dang rang gis tshan nyid mkhyen pas na /
NG0265:14223: shin tu bzang ba'i chos nyid mchog dang ldan /
NG0265:14225: mchog sbyin pas sgrub pa po la dngos grub rnams
NG0265:14226: kyi nang nas mu stegs kyi dngos grub las khyad
NG0265:14227: byas pas na go 'phang mchog chos sku brnyes pa
NG0265:14229: khams 'dod khams gnas rigs nyi shu gzugs khams bcu bdun /
NG0265:14230: gzugs med skye mched mu bzhi gang bsgrub pa byed la chos sku ston pa'o /
NG0265:14231: gsum kun la rtag tu dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad /
NG0265:14232: 'gro ba'i / mgon po dus gsum sgrib pa med
NG0265:14233: par me long dag pa'i byad ltar gsal ba rab
NG0265:14234: mkhyen pa'o // dam tshig mchog sku'i dam tshig sku
NG0265:14235: mi zad pa rgyan gyi 'khor lo'i mtshon nas de
NG0265:14236: bzhin du gsung thugs la yang sbyor /
NG0265:14237: gsung dngos grub dam pa bdag la stsol /
NG0265:14239: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi /
NG0265:14241: yang dag pa ye shes kyi sgo nas yon tan rgya chen te /
NG0265:14244: lan cig tsam ni brjod pas kyang *//
NG0265:14245: sangs rgyas thams cad 'grub nas dngos grub stsol bar 'gyur /
NG0265:14246: ni mang du bstod na lta ci smos zhes so //
NG0265:14247: de nas rgyal ba thams cad gnyis su med par sgrub pa 'di gsungs so /
NG0265:14249: bsnyen pa'i don du bzlas pa 'di dag bya //
NG0265:14252: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs ka nyid /
NG0265:14253: bdag rdo rje sems dpar gsal ba'i thugs ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang du /
NG0265:14254: nyi dkyil rgya long tsam cig bsam /
NG0265:14255: de'i steng du dz+nya na sa twa hu~m zhes pas
NG0265:14256: ye shes sems dpa' dkar po tshon gang ba ral
NG0265:14257: pa'i thor tshugs can cig bsgom /
NG0265:14258: de'i thugs kar zla dkyil gyi steng du rdo rje
NG0265:14259: nas tsam gyi bum pa la hu~m nyung 'bru tsam
NG0265:14260: cig bsgom / de'i tha mar hu~m badzra d+h+r-ika / ces pas bskor bar bsam //
NG0265:14261: gsang ba'i sngags don bsgom par bya //
NG0265:14262: de bzhin yum la'ang yum gyi thugs kar ye shes sems dpa'i thugs kar dril bu mum @#//
NG0265:14264: de'i tha mar mum d+ha twi shwa ris bskor bar bsgom /
NG0265:14266: rigs bzhi yab yum bsgom pa dang */
NG0265:14267: de bzhin rigs bzhi yang yum la rang gi phyag mtshan mtshan sa bon sngags kyis bskor bar bsgom //
NG0265:14268: sems dpa' zla ba'i 'od dang bcas //
NG0265:14269: sems dpa' thams cad kyi thugs kar zla dkyil re
NG0265:14270: de'i steng du 'od dkar po tshon gang ba re'i
NG0265:14271: rtse la rang rang gi bskyed sngags rtsa sngags kyis
NG0265:14272: bskor bar bsgom // kun bzang yab yum sngags don bsgom //
NG0265:14273: gtso bo rdo rje sems dpa' dang mthun no //
NG0265:14274: thub pa rnams thugs kar pad+ma 'i steng du 'od
NG0265:14275: ser po mtheb long tsam re la sngags kyis bskor
NG0265:14277: sgo ba rnams la nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor re la 'od mthing ga'i 'od /
NG0265:14278: mthe bong tsam re la sngags kyis bskor ba dang */
NG0265:14279: lha rnams kyi dung khang du zla ba la /
NG0265:14280: om dang ljags steng du pad+ma la ahste thugs kar hu~m sogs gong ltar ro bcas /
NG0265:14281: bdag dam tshig sems dpa' dang lha ye shes sems
NG0265:14282: dpa' gnyis med me long nang gi gzugs dang byad
NG0265:14283: 'dra ba'o // dkyil 'khor gnyis kyis tshul bzung bsgom /
NG0265:14285: om bo d+hi tsit+ta ma ha su kha dz+nya na
NG0265:14286: d+ha tu ah byang chub kyi sems bde ba chen
NG0265:14288: de nas hu~m bi shwa bi shud+d+he phat dzahzhes brjod de /
NG0265:14289: de las mar me gcig las gnyis su bye ba
NG0265:14290: ltar mdun gyi nam mkha' la dkyil 'khor gnyis su
NG0265:14291: phye las 'phro 'du bya zhing bzlas pa bya rtog
NG0265:14292: tshogs sbyang */ sku gsung thugs mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo //
NG0265:14293: mchog dang grub chen brgyad la sogs pa /
NG0265:14296: smon lam rab tu gdab par bya //
NG0265:14297: ye gdod ma na nas 'khor 'das mnyam nyid chos sku'i ngang du dag par gnas pa la /
NG0265:14299: ma rig pa'i dbang gis yod pa la sgro dang med pa la skur btab ste //
NG0265:14300: de bzlog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam mnos nas //
NG0265:14301: sgro skur gzung 'dzin gyis bsags pa'i lus ngag yid
NG0265:14302: la gnas pa'i sgrib pa rnams bzlog par bya ba'i
NG0265:14303: don du rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor du zhugs nas dam
NG0265:14306: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs kyi thugs dang ci 'gal ba /
NG0265:14308: sangs rgyas thugs rje'i bdag nyid yin pas //
NG0265:14309: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig dang 'gal ba rnams /
NG0265:14311: ye shes rgyal po sangs rgyas sku rnam snang gsung snang mtha' thugs /
NG0265:14314: yon tan phrin las don grub de re re la yang snga po tshang bas na /
NG0265:14316: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor ba //
NG0265:14317: dus da lta nyid du lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs dang mnyam par sbyor ba //
NG0265:14318: de nyid du ni sku gsung thugs kyi sid+d+hi bdag la stsol //
NG0265:14319: zhes sangs rgyas thams cad kyis ched du gsungs so //
NG0265:14320: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba rnams kyis 'od min du
NG0265:14321: gsungs pa las gsang bdag gis dam pa'i rigs can
NG0265:14323: de nas gsungs so zhes sbrel gang gis gsungs na /
NG0265:14324: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa 'das
NG0265:14325: pa ma lus shing ma byon pa lus pa med
NG0265:14326: pa da ltar ba thams cad kyis /
NG0265:14327: gang gi don du gsungs na //
NG0265:14328: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug dam pa rnams kyi don /
NG0265:14331: yang dag pa rgyun gyi rnal @#//
NG0265:14333: de ting bsgom pa stong pa nyid de chos thams cad de kho na nyid stong pa nyid do //
NG0265:14335: mi dmigs chos dbyings de bzhin nyid //
NG0265:14336: rang bzhin 'od gsal kun tu snang *//
NG0265:14337: kun tu snang zhing khyab pa'i snying rje'i 'od kyi kun tu gdal ba'o //
NG0265:14338: kun la snang ba snying rje sgyu ma'o //
NG0265:14340: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin a dkar por bsgom mo //
NG0265:14341: gzhal yas khang gzhung dang lha tshogs 'byung ba'i rgyu'o //
NG0265:14343: e yam rlung bam chu sum sa lam ri rab ram me b+h+rum /
NG0265:14345: b+h+rum las rin chen gzhal yas khang *//
NG0265:14346: dbus 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi gru chad blo 'bur bar khyams sgo dang bcas pa bskyed do //
NG0265:14348: seng ge rnam snang glang rin 'byung rta mtha' yas rma bya te'u /
NG0265:14350: dkyil 'khor bsam yas lhun gyis grub /
NG0265:14351: sangs rgyas zhe gnyis rang rang gi sngags gong nas 'byung ba ltar brjod la bsgom par bya'o //
NG0265:14352: lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu //
NG0265:14353: phyag rgya bzhi yis spyan drangs nas //
NG0265:14354: rang snang bzhi bcu phyag 'tshal zhing *//
NG0265:14355: phyag 'tshal ba'i se gol dkrol la brda dang bcas pas /
NG0265:14356: dam tshig dkyil 'khor gyi ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NG0265:14357: la ma 'gags pa'i sgo nas phyag 'tshal zhing ma
NG0265:14358: skyes pa'i sgo nas gnyis su med par bya'o //
NG0265:14359: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed cing *//
NG0265:14362: ye shes thugs rjes chen po bdag la dgongs nas kyang */
NG0265:14364: mi dmigs pa bsgrub pa'i don du mchog gi dngos grub rnams //
NG0265:14365: chos sku thob par bya ba //
NG0265:14366: bdag la stsal zhing dngos grub ma thob bar du brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NG0265:14367: sku mdog zhal ni rnam par bsgyur /
NG0265:14368: rang zhal phyag gsal bar bsgom zhing *//
NG0265:14369: phyag rgya pad skor g.yas g.yon dbus dang gsum du
NG0265:14370: bskor lha rnams yud tsam gyis yid la gsal bar
NG0265:14371: bya // sku ni gar thabs glog 'gyu ba //
NG0265:14372: rtsa ba'i lha zhe gnyis su gsal ba mnyes pa'i lha rnams //
NG0265:14373: phyag rgya'am gar gyi mchod pa 'bul //
NG0265:14374: mchod pa bzhes dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NG0265:14376: dang me tog ma sngo mar me ma dmar dri /
NG0265:14377: chab ma ljang gus mchod pa'o //
NG0265:14378: bdud rtsis mchod la dngos grub blang *//
NG0265:14379: rang byung gdod nas dag pa yi //
NG0265:14380: rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NG0265:14381: rigs lnga ye shes lnga yi dngos //
NG0265:14382: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NG0265:14383: bcom ldan rigs lnga yab yum dang *//
NG0265:14384: byang chub lcam dral thub pa drug / kun bzang yab yum 'khor bcas la //
NG0265:14385: bla med bdud rtsi'i mchod pa 'bul //
NG0265:14386: thugs rjes cher dgongs dbang dang dngos grub rtsol //
NG0265:14387: ar+g+ham me tog bdug spos dang *//
NG0265:14388: mar me dri chab bshos dang sgra //
NG0265:14389: ting nge 'dzin gyis re re la gong du bshad pa'i //
NG0265:14390: phyi nang gsang bar sbyar ba rnams //
NG0265:14391: bdag gi phung po khams skye mched dang mnyam pa'i lha tshogs la 'bul //
NG0265:14392: rgyal ba'i rigs lnga'i sras sems dpa' rnams kyi dang thugs kyi dpal be'u nas /
NG0265:14394: dngos grub stsal ba dang dang stsol bar sgrub pa pos len par don dam par mi dmigs kyang *//
NG0265:14395: sngon gyi sems can la dngos grub sby-in par thugs dam du bzhes pa'i dbang gis dngos grub rtsol /
NG0265:14396: cig / tshogs 'dod yon drug dang gtor ma dang bdud rtsi @#//
NG0265:14399: ta na sgrol ba dang ga na la sogs ci 'byor pa /
NG0265:14401: ting 'dzin yid kyis mchod pa mang por spros nas /
NG0265:14404: rgyal ba dgongs pa rgya mtsho ltar gnas pa rnams kyis bzhes su gsol /
NG0265:14406: chos kyi sku skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin las /
NG0265:14409: gzugs kyi sku sgyu ma'i ltar snang la rang bzhin med pa skye ba'i skur ston pa /
NG0265:14411: thugs rjes sems can kun la khyab pa don byed pa //
NG0265:14412: rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su snang ba la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0265:14413: de nas gnyis med sgrub don du //
NG0265:14414: sngags bzla bar bya ste sgom thabs ni gong ltar byas la /
NG0265:14416: spyi dang khyad par badzra d+h+r-ika la sogs pa bsnyen 'dzab dbul //
NG0265:14417: de nas zhugs mar gtsigs pa yi //
NG0265:14418: sgrub pa zab mo yang dag bshad //
NG0265:14419: de bzhin nyid dang ni om yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid //
NG0265:14420: dang por chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NG0265:14421: dmigs pa med pa'i don gyis bsgom //
NG0265:14422: dmigs med chos dbyings de bzhin nyid //
NG0265:14423: om ma ha su kha hu~m zhes pas chos nyid stong par bsgoms te /
NG0265:14424: lung 'di nyid nas tshig bsdus nas bsgom mo /
NG0265:14426: om sangs rgyas bde chen kun 'dus pa //
NG0265:14427: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis //
NG0265:14428: thams cad kun 'dus khyab par bya //
NG0265:14429: rang bzhin 'od gsal kun tu snang *//
NG0265:14430: tsit+ta pra be sha s+pha ra na phat /
NG0265:14431: lung 'di nas bsdus snying rje sgyu ma bsgam mo //
NG0265:14432: rgyu yi ting 'dzin rab ldan pas //
NG0265:14433: om rnam 'byor zab mo sku gsum rdzogs //
NG0265:14434: med pa'i rgyu las mngon gsal ba'i //
NG0265:14435: sems kyi rang bzhin ye shes gsal //
NG0265:14436: rgyu yi yi ge a dkar gsal //
NG0265:14438: e yam bam sum lam ram lnga las bskyed //
NG0265:14440: e a ka sha man+da la zhes pas nam mkha' gru gsum bsgom /
NG0265:14441: om karma rak+sha ham gis rlung zla kham /
NG0265:14442: bam ma ma ki ri man+dal zhes pa bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho bsgom //
NG0265:14443: nam mkha' rlung dang bdud rtsi mtsho /
NG0265:14444: lam tish+tha man+da la zhes pas //
NG0265:14445: rin chen sa gzhi sum su me ru sum gyis rin po che'i /
NG0265:14447: ram dz+nya na dz+wa la man+dal la zhes pas //
NG0265:14448: ye shes me 'od kun tu gsal //
NG0265:14449: b+h+rum b+h+rum cir yang gyur pa'i yig 'bru bsam zhes
NG0265:14450: brjod de gzhal yas khang dbus zla kham sgo gcig
NG0265:14451: pa gru chad kyi sgo dang ngo *//
NG0265:14454: seng ge sa btegs pa nyi ma zla ba pad+ma'i gdan gyi steng */
NG0265:14456: yid bzhin rin chen gyis rgyan dang gdan rin po che'i khri rkang gi rgyan gsal //
NG0265:14457: nam mkha'i dkyil la ye shes sems dpa' rlung gis btegs pa phab /
NG0265:14459: 'phros bskul don byas 'dus gsal bar cho ga gsum gyis bskyed do /
NG0265:14461: rdo rje sems dpa' yab zhal gsum phyag drug yum zhal gcig phyag gnyis gong ltar /
NG0265:14463: ye shes lnga yi dbang om ma ha shu+u n+ya ta la sogs /
NG0265:14465: om sarba ta tha ga ta la sogs //
NG0265:14466: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab /
NG0265:14470: rtags kyi yab yum dam tshig gi phyag rgya /
NG0265:14471: mkha' gsang las kyi phyag rgya //
NG0265:14472: sbyor ba chos kyi phyag rgya /
NG0265:14475: chos kyi sku phyag rgya chen por bzhugs par bsgom / @#//
NG0265:14476: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum bsgom pa ni //
NG0265:14477: lam kun ma nor bar gsang sngags kyi /
NG0265:14479: yum chos dbyings ye shes las spyan drangs //
NG0265:14480: stong nyid ye shes me long las //
NG0265:14482: ma skyes pa las gzugs sku /
NG0265:14483: mi 'gag par gzugs skur snang ba /
NG0265:14485: mkha' la ye shes 'ja' tshon 'dra bar snang ba ji bzhin du /
NG0265:14487: dbyings nas ye shes kyi sku'i /
NG0265:14488: phyag rgyar spyan drangs pas gshegs su gsol / ! dbyings nyid rang bzhin rnam par dag pa las //
NG0265:14489: thugs rje'i dbang gis sprul pa'i skur bzhengs pa //
NG0265:14491: sangs rgyas kun 'dus mi skyod yab yum gtso //
NG0265:14492: rang snang thugs rje che la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0265:14493: legs par sems can don phyir nan tan mchog cing *//
NG0265:14496: mi bskyod mthing ga dkar dmar zhal /
NG0265:14497: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen g.yas //
NG0265:14498: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NG0265:14500: yab yum gnyis su med pa la //
NG0265:14502: ye shes ngang las dngos grub stsol //
NG0265:14503: bdud rtsis mchod rang byung gdong nas rnam par dag / rtsa brgyad stong la sbyar ba'i sman //
NG0265:14504: ye shes lnga rdzogs sgrub rdzas 'di /
NG0265:14506: gsang dri med rnams dag gi nan sgrengs la sngags kyis gtor ma dbul //
NG0265:14507: bde gshegs rgyal ba yab yum la //
NG0265:14508: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NG0265:14509: thugs rjes dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NG0265:14510: bzhes nas kun tu dgyes mdzad la //
NG0265:14511: 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NG0265:14513: chos sku skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin las //
NG0265:14514: gzugs sku sgyu ma'i skyes bu'i tshul bstan nas //
NG0265:14515: thugs rjes kun la khyab pa'i don mdzad pa //
NG0265:14516: yi dam rgyal ba'i sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NG0265:14517: bstod cing 'dzab badzra d+h-ika bzlas bshags pa bya //
NG0265:14518: tshogs mchod dang dam tshig bskang bshags nyin gung mtshan gung tshig gi tshogs mchod /
NG0265:14520: rang gzhan don du chos sku theb par //
NG0265:14521: smon lam yongs su gdab par bya'o //
NG0265:14523: dpal khrag 'thung gi gal po las /
NG0265:14524: chos nyid zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor te /
NG0265:14526: / de nas sangs rgyas thams cad kyi mnga' bdag
NG0265:14527: gi khro bo 'byung ba'i ru tra chen po 'di
NG0265:14528: dag gsungs so // rtag pa rang rgyud ru tra ni //
NG0265:14529: mos pa rjes su bzhag shes la //
NG0265:14530: skyes bu yul gyi 'dod pas gdungs /
NG0265:14532: log pa'i dbang gis nyon mongs lnga //
NG0265:14533: dang po log pa'i dbang gis nyon mongs pa lngar brtags pa'i rang rgyud pa ni /
NG0265:14534: dngos po thams cad rang gi ngo bo phyogs dang bral ba la /
NG0265:14535: rig pa'i rkyen dang bral bas don ma mthong zhing */
NG0265:14536: dngos med la dngos por bzung bas rig pa la
NG0265:14537: dngos por zhen cing brtags pas rang rgyud par snang
NG0265:14538: ngo *// brtags pa'i dbang gis gzung 'dzin du //
NG0265:14539: brtags pa'i rang rgyud pa ni /
NG0265:14540: gang la de dag med pa la /
NG0265:14541: de dang der zhen cing chags pa ni /
NG0265:14543: yul dang shes pa tha dad du gyur pa'i phyir ro //
NG0265:14544: brtags pa ni dngos po bzhi la don ma shes pas dngos po gsum du brtags pa'o //
NG0265:14545: zhen pa'i dbang gis 'dod yon lnga /
NG0265:14546: brtags pa'i rang rgyus pa ni zhen pa ste //
NG0265:14547: med pa la brtag pas gnyis su 'khrul la phyi rol rang dang @#//
NG0265:14548: mthun pa'i yul lngas glo bur rang rgyud par rgyun du+u skye zhing 'jug pa'i phyir rtags pa'o //
NG0265:14549: brtags pas ji bzhin ji bzhin pa ni thams cad du khyab par gnas kyang */
NG0265:14551: long ba rang la shes pa ma skyes pa ltar gzhan las byung ba ma yin no /
NG0265:14553: pa de yang gong ma gsum po ma shes pas lan no //
NG0265:14555: bdag dang bdag gir 'dzin pas na /
NG0265:14556: khams gsum 'khor ba'i grong khyer brgyud //
NG0265:14557: nam mkha' dang chu la dngos por zhen pa ltar /
NG0265:14558: rig pa ma skyes pa'i rang bzhin la /
NG0265:14559: nga'am bdag ces 'dzin pa'i phyir bdag tu mthong ba'o //
NG0265:14560: de'i dbang gis phung po bzhi dang */
NG0265:14563: longs spyod la bdag zhen mngon par brtags so //
NG0265:14564: de dag kyang chu las rlabs bzhin no //
NG0265:14565: ji skad bshad pa yang bdag tu 'dzin cing brtags te /
NG0265:14566: mngon par zhen pas bdag gis khams gsum du yang 'khor ba'i grong khyer brgyud pa /
NG0265:14567: nam mkha'i mthas gtugs pa'i 'gro ba rnams /
NG0265:14568: khams gsum du skye zhing grong khyer du brgyud do //
NG0265:14570: sngon tshe dus nam byung na /
NG0265:14573: sangs rgyas srid pa'i sgron mar byung */
NG0265:14574: bla ma gang las dam nyams na //
NG0265:14575: slob dpon rgyal ba'i 'khor lo yi //
NG0265:14578: gsang sngags blta ba dam tshig / spyod pa /
NG0265:14584: don de gdeng du ma gyur cing */
NG0265:14586: srog gcod ma byin len mi tshangs spyod rdzun dang bzhi rang rgyud par //
NG0265:14587: log pa'i lung du spyad pa yis //
NG0265:14588: dmyal ba tsha grang yi dwags phyi nang sgrib pa can /
NG0265:14590: tha mar las kyi srin por ra tra ma skyes /
NG0265:14591: khams gsum 'khrugs pa'i bdud du gyur //
NG0265:14592: dang po gang las byung ba med //
NG0265:14593: tha ma gang du 'gag med la //
NG0265:14594: gzhi las 'khrul pa rang rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas
NG0265:14595: pa de dag gi rang bzhin ji lta bu zhe
NG0265:14596: na / gang gi phyir dngos po'i snying po de
NG0265:14597: kho na nyid thogs tha mar med pa'i ye shes
NG0265:14599: de las byung ba'i 'khrul pa dang ma 'khrul pa'i
NG0265:14600: rgyu dang 'bras bur bcas pa'i chos ni nam mkha'
NG0265:14601: ltar dang po gang las kyang 'ong ba med /
NG0265:14602: bar du gang na 'ang gnas pa med /
NG0265:14603: tha ma gang du+u 'ang 'gag cing 'dzin pa med cing chu dang rlabs bzhin no //
NG0265:14604: de'i phyir 'khrul pa'i rgyu dang ngo bo dang 'bras
NG0265:14605: bur bcas pa ni ji ltar snang yang rang rgyud
NG0265:14606: pa med de / de dag gi rang bzhin ma spangs par de dag las ma 'das pa ni /
NG0265:14607: rang bzhin nam chos nyid do //
NG0265:14608: bdag gzhan 'dzin pas sngon smin te //
NG0265:14609: ngo bo ma rtogs pa'i dbang gis bdag gzhan du 'dzin pa la /
NG0265:14611: sgrib pa dang las nyon gyi 'bras bu duhkha zhen
NG0265:14612: pa dang bcas pa nyid sngon du smin te 'khrul
NG0265:14613: pa'i 'gro ba de dag gi ngo la /
NG0265:14614: zhen pa ma log cing bden pa mngon du ma
NG0265:14615: byas kyi bar du skad cig ma tsam du'ang bde
NG0265:14616: ba med la / thar pa dang thams cad mkhyen
NG0265:14617: pa'i skal ba yang med ces bya ba'i don to
NG0265:14618: ba med la / // skad cig bde dang thar pa med //
NG0265:14619: ma rtogs zhen pa'i 'gro ba dag / dper na
NG0265:14620: sems can gyi don ma rtogs pa rnams kyis ma
NG0265:14621: shes par zos pas dug gi na ba lta bu
NG0265:14622: dang *// zas la dug gis btab pa'am /
NG0265:14624: ri dwags smig rgyu la chur 'khrul na smig rgyu la /
NG0265:14627: sdug bsngal nyid las thar ba med /
NG0265:14628: de khams gsum 'khor bar 'khyams par gyur pa'o //
NG0265:14629: des brtags pa dang rang rgyud kyi ru tra bshad zin to //
NG0265:14630: sprul pa 'dod pa bskang ba'i ru tra yis //
NG0265:14631: bsam pa yid dang 'thad shes pa //
NG0265:14632: sna tshogs me tog gling phyin pa 'dra /
NG0265:14635: rdo rje slob dpon gyi smon lam gyi stobs kyis /
NG0265:14636: slob dpon rgyal ba'i 'khor lo ste rdo rje snying po dang */
NG0265:14637: slob ma dge slong nag po sngon byung la snang la /
NG0265:14638: da lta slob dpon dang slob ma rnams kyang */
NG0265:14639: las dang smon lam gyis phrad pa'i phyir ro //
NG0265:14640: dngos dpal chen nyid sprul pa 'dod pa skong ba'i ru tra yin no //
NG0265:14641: las dang smon lam mthun dbang gis //
NG0265:14642: byin rlabs gang zhus bla ma la //
NG0265:14643: gdug pa ru tra 'dul ba'i phyir //
NG0265:14644: gang sprul pa ni brgyud pa rang thabs kyi byin rlabs dang */
NG0265:14645: cho ga 'am man ngag gi byin rlabs dang dam tshig / blta ba /
NG0265:14647: nyams kyis bstan pa'i brtags pa'i snang ba bral zhing
NG0265:14648: ye shes kyi snang ba 'char bar nus la de
NG0265:14649: ni ting nge 'dzin dang tha mi dad do //
NG0265:14651: sangs rgyas rnams 'dus nas ru tra 'dul bar bka' bgros bcas /
NG0265:14654: cho 'phrul kyis 'dul bar bskul ba byas nas ni /
NG0265:14656: las bzhi rdo rje bskos la btab //
NG0265:14657: da ltar gyi ni man ngag dang ldan pa'i slob dpon la bya'o //
NG0265:14658: rigs ngais dang ldan shes rab can //
NG0265:14659: las dang thugs rjes phrad rung la //
NG0265:14660: 'dir sngon byung du ru tra nyid la bya ste /
NG0265:14661: lta spyod zab mo la gnas shing */
NG0265:14662: bla mas byin brlabs pas rigs nges pa dang lus
NG0265:14663: kyi phyi nang gang la yang ma chags par rtogs
NG0265:14664: pas dad pa dang ldan pa dang */
NG0265:14665: sangs rgyas zhal mthong zhing skad cig mas bden pa mthong bas shes rab can no //
NG0265:14666: sngon nas sbyangs shing bsags pa'i las dang */
NG0265:14667: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs rjes btul nas sa la bzhugs pas phrad rung la zhes so //
NG0265:14668: gzhan du na bla ma dang theg pa chen po'i rigs su nges pa dang */
NG0265:14669: dad pa dang dam tshig dang ldan pa snying rje che ba /
NG0265:14670: yid mi skyo ba shes rab che ba /
NG0265:14671: gtong phod cing brtson 'grus che ba /
NG0265:14672: rang gi las dag pa dang */
NG0265:14673: bla mas de ltar rtogs pas thugs rje skye ba'i yul du gyur pas phrad du rung ba'o //
NG0265:14674: rang bzhin dag pa'i las dbang gis //
NG0265:14675: dug gis dug nad bsal ba ltar //
NG0265:14677: de'i phyir na thog ma bar dang tha ma'i rang bzhin la brtags pa dang */
NG0265:14678: bde ba chen po la brtags pas /
NG0265:14679: dug lnga gang nus pas chos nyid du 'gyur ro //
NG0265:14680: dngos po gang btab pas gzung pa'i yul nub /
NG0265:14681: de'i ngo bo mthong bas 'dzin pa'i sems nus ste /
NG0265:14682: chos thams cad nam mkha' ltar gsal bar 'gyur ro //
NG0265:14683: spyod yul lha'i rang bzhin la brtags pa dang */
NG0265:14684: dbang po de bar nus pa la brtags pa dang */
NG0265:14685: 'dod pa lnga sgyu mar skye ba'i thabs kyi grub kyis //
NG0265:14686: man ngag dang bral ba'i rtog pas ni ma yin no //
NG0265:14687: ma lus pas na spyod yul gyi chos thams cad do //
NG0265:14688: bshad thabs dais 'dul bar 'gyur ba ni chu rlabs zhi ba bzhin no //
NG0265:14690: rlabs la nyam nga ba med pa ltar /
NG0265:14691: snang ba sems nyid ma bcos par shes na dran
NG0265:14692: rtog dang snang ba gang la yang dgag bsgrub dang
NG0265:14693: bral ba'o // ma lus thabs kyis 'dul bar 'gyur //
NG0265:14694: rang nyid gang zhen cing dag pa ni //
NG0265:14697: gzung 'dzin dang gang la zhen pa dag go / des @#//
NG0265:14698: bsgyur ba'i sgo gsum gyi bya ba ni /
NG0265:14700: thabs ni de dag nyid do //
NG0265:14701: de dag gis ji ltar grol zhe na /
NG0265:14702: dug gi dug nad bsal ba ltar te /
NG0265:14703: blun po 'chi bar byed pa'i dug nad de /
NG0265:14704: dug la sngags kyis btab pas sel ba ltar /
NG0265:14705: theg pa chung ba nad kyi gzir ba'i chags sdang
NG0265:14706: la sogs pa ni thabs khyad par can de nyid
NG0265:14707: / ye shes su rang grol bar 'gyur ro //
NG0265:14708: sprul pa'i khrag 'thung cir yang snang *//
NG0265:14709: cir yang snang bar sprul pas te /
NG0265:14710: thugs kyi rigs gcig pu'i khrag 'thung ma nges par cir yang snang ba ni /
NG0265:14711: ru tra 'dul ba'i phyir khro bo 'dul byed kyi tshogs su yang snang ste //
NG0265:14714: mthing nag g.yas dkar dang g.yon dmar ba'i dbus /
NG0265:14716: rdo rje bar ma na zhing mchog gi dbyug pa
NG0265:14717: tha ma na kha t+wam ga / g.yon dang po
NG0265:14718: // dril bu bar ma na b+han+d+ha tha ma na ba su'i zhags /
NG0265:14720: yum yab kyi sku dang mthun pa dang gnyis su med par 'khril /
NG0265:14722: yang ni thugs kyi he ru ka ru tra'i tshogs 'di ltar yang snang bar 'gyur /
NG0265:14725: bskal pa 'jigs pa dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar ba'i me dpung gi dbus na yi //
NG0265:14726: 'od zer 'du bas dngos grub ster 'phro'i klong dkyil na /
NG0265:14727: gnas kyi sems can gyi don mdzad pas /
NG0265:14729: sku ni 'dul ba'i dbang du gyur pa'i phyir /
NG0265:14730: dud ka gting dpag dka' ba'i phyir chen po ste /
NG0265:14732: zhal gsum grub po la phyag drug po //
NG0265:14733: phar phyin drug gi don mdzad pas /
NG0265:14735: gnag dud ka dang g.yas gti mug 'dul mthing dang g.yon 'dod chags 'dul dmar ba'i dbu //
NG0265:14736: g.yas pa gsum na thogs pa ni //
NG0265:14737: g.yas dang po na dgra bgegs la brdeg pa'i dang ma mo mkha' 'gro 'bod pa'i g.yab mo //
NG0265:14738: ti ra'i dbyug pa chen po dang *//
NG0265:14740: rdo rjes g.yon thod khrag dkrug cing zhal du gsol ba dang */
NG0265:14741: tha ma na khyung gi khra chen ru tra'i tshogs la spor zhing 'gyed pa'o //
NG0265:14742: g.yon gyi gsum na thogs pa ni //
NG0265:14743: ti ra'i rgyu ma'i zhags pa dang */
NG0265:14746: thod rlon dmar gyis bkang ba dang */
NG0265:14749: ti ra phra mo'i chung ngu khog pa nas //
NG0265:14750: glo snying nang grol phyung nas 'byin cing za /
NG0265:14751: gti mug gnas su dag pas sku la //
NG0265:14752: glang chen gyi ko rlon gos su gon /
NG0265:14753: 'dod chags ma spangs gnas su dag pas //
NG0265:14754: zhing lpags g.yang gzhi'i sham thabs can /
NG0265:14756: thod rlon phreng ba rgyan du byas /
NG0265:14757: kro d+hi shwa ri sku la thabs shes rab mi 'bral bas 'khril /
NG0265:14759: gdug pa thams cad 'dul bar byed //
NG0265:14760: yang ni sprul pa'i he ru ka gdul bya la 'di ltar snang ste /
NG0265:14762: dkar dang dbus mthing ga g.yon dmar ba'i mdog / g.yas kyi phyag na bsnams pa ni /
NG0265:14763: dang po na gnyis med mtshon pa'i //
NG0265:14764: rdo rje zhing bar ma na sgrol ba mtshon pa'i dbyug tha ma na rbaud gtong mdzad pa'i /
NG0265:14767: thod khrag bar ma na dug gsum 'jom pa'i kha t+wam dam nyams 'ching ba'i rgyu zhags bsnams /
NG0265:14769: yum dang gnyis su med par sku la 'khril /
NG0265:14771: yang ni sprul pa'i he ru
NG0265:14775: g.yas dkar gsal ba'i nyams g.yon dmar bde ba'i nyams smug nag dbus /
NG0265:14777: g.yas kyi dang po ti ra la /
NG0265:14778: zhing dbyug / bar ma rdo rje b+han+d+ha tha //
NG0265:14779: g.yon gyi dang po 'ching ba'i rgyu zhags la //
NG0265:14780: bar ma dam nyams gdug par 'gyed pa'i khyung gi khra chen po //
NG0265:14781: tha ma ti ra'i glo snying nang rol 'dren /
NG0265:14783: yum dang gnyis su med pa'o //
NG0265:14784: yab ni sprul pa 'di ltar snang *//
NG0265:14785: g.yas longs sku dkar dbus chos sku smug g.yon sprul sku dmar zhal /
NG0265:14787: rdo rje bar kha t+wam tha ma cang te'u g.yas /
NG0265:14789: dung dmar bar rgyu zhags tha ma khyung khra g.yon //
NG0265:14790: yum dang thabs shes gnyis su med pa la //
NG0265:14791: dur khrod chas brgyad rnams sku la rdzogs //
NG0265:14792: yang ni sprul pas 'dod pa skong */
NG0265:14794: g.yas dkar thugs rje chags pas /
NG0265:14795: g.yon dmar mi 'gyur bas dbus mthing nag dang po /
NG0265:14796: rdo rje bar khyung khra tha ma zhing dbyug g.yas /
NG0265:14798: dung chen bar zhing dbyug tha ma rgyu ma'i zhags pa g.yon //
NG0265:14799: yum dang gnyis su med par 'khril //
NG0265:14800: gdug pa ru tra'i tshogs thams cad dbang du bsdus nas zhabs kyis gzir /
NG0265:14802: yang ni 'di ltar sprul pa 'dod pa skong ba'i ru tra dpal chen po'i tshogs /
NG0265:14804: g.yas dkar ba stong nyid dbus smug mtshan ma med pa g.yon pa dmar /
NG0265:14807: zhing dbyug bar rdo rje tha ma khyung khra ni spor /
NG0265:14809: zhags pa bar dung chen te thod pa tha mar ro dbyug g.yon //
NG0265:14810: yum dang thabs shes gnyis su med pa la //
NG0265:14811: gdul bya ru tra'i tshogs 'dul ba'i he ru ka
NG0265:14812: / yang ni sprul pa 'dod pa skong ba'i khrag
NG0265:14814: sku mdog dmar khams gsum dbang du sdud pas smug zhal gsum la //
NG0265:14815: g.yas pa thabs dkar la g.yon pa shes rab mi
NG0265:14816: 'gyur nag / phyag bzhi g.yas g.yon dang po na
NG0265:14818: rdo rje g.yon thod khrag dkrug cing gsol /
NG0265:14821: 'og ma dril bu g.yas kha t+wam ga / yum dang bde stong gnyis su med pa ste /
NG0265:14823: rdo rje ru tra zhes te gdul bya'i ming 'dul byed la btags /
NG0265:14825: stong gsum gyi 'jig rten khams rnams kyang thugs kyi he ru ka / sa gang ba'i dpe //
NG0265:14826: nam mkha'i rdul phra rab dang mnyam pa'i grangs //
NG0265:14827: ting nge 'dzin ye shes su langs pa ni /
NG0265:14829: sna tshogs dang po rang gi ngo bo nyams dang ldan pa ste /
NG0265:14831: rgya mtsho rin chen sna tshogs kyi gling */
NG0265:14833: phyin na rin po che'i rigs bsam yas pa /
NG0265:14834: ltar bshad pa khyed la bstan //
NG0265:14835: sngon nas zhen pa'i bag chags dag / ru tra
NG0265:14836: de'i thog ma med pa nas da lta yan chad
NG0265:14837: kyi skye ba sna tshogs las gyur pa'i bag chags
NG0265:14838: dang sgo gsum gyis spyod pa dang khyad par gsang
NG0265:14839: ba log par gol ba ste /
NG0265:14840: de dag gi bag chags dag pa'o //
NG0265:14841: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba'i //
NG0265:14842: 'das pa ni sngon yang ru tra nag po gsang ba las gol bas /
NG0265:14843: dang po rang rgyud pa la zhen cing nyon mongs pa la spyod pa ste /
NG0265:14844: dngos po'i don ma rtogs par nor bar gyur to //
NG0265:14847: gang de ltar log par gol ba ste tshar bcad pa'i phyir /
NG0265:14848: phrin las bzhis rim par btul zhing tshar bcad nas /
NG0265:14849: mthong lam skyes shing dbugs phyin pa'o //
NG0265:14850: de la sbyor ba byas pas sngon gyi las ci spyad dran zhing gsal bar gyur to //
NG0265:14851: nor pas yid ches 'gyod pa nyid //
NG0265:14852: de phyir sngar ldan gyi las dang */
NG0265:14853: lta spyod log pa la log par shes shing the tshom za bas gdung ba dang */
NG0265:14855: sngar rang gi las spyad pa rnams nor bar shes pas /
NG0265:14856: dpal gyis sgrib pa sbyangs pas /
NG0265:14858: gang de phyis 'jug med pa'i sems //
NG0265:14859: gal te sngar gyi bya ba log par shes nas
NG0265:14860: de'i nyes pa khong du chud pas 'khrul pa phyis
NG0265:14861: mi skye bas // skye ba dang las shes /
NG0265:14862: skye ba sngon du gyur pas phyis der mi 'jug pa'i sems skyes pa'o //
NG0265:14863: gdung bas zhen pa mngon bsal nas //
NG0265:14864: gang gi shugs kyis gdung ba ni /
NG0265:14865: gdung ba de sngar gyi las nyon dang sgrib pa'i
NG0265:14866: bag chags yun ring por bsags pa la mngon par
NG0265:14867: zhen pa'o // de mngon du bsal ba ni /
NG0265:14868: rtogs pa dang ting nge 'dzin spyod pa'i gdung ba drag pos nyes pa bsal bas zhal mthong ste //
NG0265:14869: bla mar drin bsab lus gdan phul //
NG0265:14870: de ltar zhal mthong bas bag chags phra ba sbyang ba'i phyir /
NG0265:14871: bla ma la drin bsab pa'i ye shes bskyed par bya ba'i phyir /
NG0265:14872: lus gdan du phul nas dgongs pa bskul bas thugs rje'i byin rlabs shar te /
NG0265:14873: chu dwangs pa dang zla ba lta bu'o //
NG0265:14874: rang sems snying po mthong ba'i rgyu //
NG0265:14877: dus dang sngar gang du skyes pa'i duhkha rnams mthong
NG0265:14878: bar byed pa'i rgyus ni dang bas rang lus gdan
NG0265:14879: du phul ba'o // da lta nyid du mthong bar snang */
NG0265:14880: zhal mthong zhing sgrib pa dag nas /
NG0265:14881: ting nge 'dzin ye shes su langs so //
NG0265:14882: bla ma dbang po thams cad la //
NG0265:14883: bla ma ni dpal rdo rje snying po he ru
NG0265:14884: ka yin la dbang po ni sangs rgyas dpag tu
NG0265:14886: dus gsum gyi slob dpon la yang 'gal ba med do //
NG0265:14889: man ngag gi brgyud pa gsum dang bral ba ni bla ma ma yin par shes par bya'o //
NG0265:14890: mnyes shing tshogs kyis gus mchod cing *//
NG0265:14891: 'dir dpal rdo rje snying por rang rang gi sgrib pa 'dag cing tshogs su gyur pa'i phyir dang */
NG0265:14892: bla ma mnyes par bya ba'i phyir dang *//
NG0265:14893: ru tra'i tshogs rnams kyi bla ma dam pa dpal
NG0265:14894: he ru ka la sku gsum thugs dang zhing mnyes
NG0265:14896: lus dang rgyan dang lag cha dang 'khor tshogs ma
NG0265:14897: lus par gus pas mchod pa mang po phul zhing
NG0265:14898: *// lus dang yo byad kun btang la //
NG0265:14899: de bzhin du dbang dang man ngag thos par 'dod
NG0265:14900: pas kyang rang gi lus bran du gzhug pa la
NG0265:14901: sogs 'khor gsum yongs su dag pas mnyes par byas
NG0265:14902: pas dbang dang man ngag 'thob pa'o //
NG0265:14903: ru tras lus gdan du phul thod skyogs bstabs so //
NG0265:14904: dkyil 'khor gsum du gzhug par bya //
NG0265:14905: rang gi snying po byang chub /
NG0265:14906: bla mas mngon du yid ches par bstan pa ni ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NG0265:14907: sangs rgyas kun gyi sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo
NG0265:14908: bstan pa ni rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil
NG0265:14909: 'khor / de gnyis rigs pa ma byung ma skyes
NG0265:14910: pa la 'jug pa ni rtsa ba byang chub kyi
NG0265:14911: 'khor / dkyil 'khor ro // dam pa gsum ldan rnal 'byor la'o //
NG0265:14912: rgyal ba kun gyi sku gsung thugs thabs chen pos
NG0265:14913: bzhag cing phog pas sems nyid nam mkha' ltar yid
NG0265:14914: la byed cing 'jug pa med pa ni /
NG0265:14916: des ru tra dkyil 'khor du gzhug cing bla ma la yon dbul bar bsten pa'o //
NG0265:14919: dug gis dug nad gso ba ltar /
NG0265:14920: nyon mongs lngas dbang bskur ba'i phyir byin gyis brlab
NG0265:14921: pa'i skye bo gang la re dogs chad pa'i dus
NG0265:14922: su / chags pa lnga'i brda gang snang ba de
NG0265:14923: dag nyid yongs su byin gyis brlab par mdzad pa'o
NG0265:14924: su / // dang po bar dang tha ma nyid //
NG0265:14926: gang gi phyir chos thams cad rang gi sems su gsal zhing */
NG0265:14927: de nyid nam mkha' ltar mthong bas dang po yang chos nyid do //
NG0265:14928: de la brda chen pos dug lnga nyid gsal ba
NG0265:14929: ngo bo stong pas de nyid chos nyid du mthong
NG0265:14930: ste de yang de nyid du rang grol bar 'gyur
NG0265:14931: ro // de dag gi dpe chu las byung ba'i chu lbur bzhin no //
NG0265:14932: ro gcig ma skyes rang bzhin gsal //
NG0265:14933: de ltar nyon mongs chos nyid du gsal ba ltar dran rtog ci byung */
NG0265:14934: gang skyes thams cad chos nyid bde ba chen por
NG0265:14935: ro gcig par 'gyur te rang bzhin gyis gsol lo
NG0265:14936: // phyin chad kun kyang de bzhin no //
NG0265:14937: de ltar rtogs pa bstan par skyes nas /
NG0265:14938: phyin chad nyon mongs lnga dang */
NG0265:14939: spyod yul dran rtog gang snang rnams ma lus pa de kho na nyid du gsal bas /
NG0265:14940: thag pa la sbrul 'dzin gyi zhen pa log pa'am /
NG0265:14941: rlabs dang chu bur ngo shes pa la dus gsum du bsal du med pa bzhin no //
NG0265:14942: phyi nang 'tsho ba'i yo byad lnga //
NG0265:14943: rig pa ma skyes pa nyid phyi rol gyi gzugs la sogs pa lngar rang bzhin shar nas /
NG0265:14944: longs spyod rgyas par gyur pa dang *//
NG0265:14945: nang thabs shes yab yum la bde ba chen po'i
NG0265:14946: longs spyod gcig la lnga rdzogs pa gsal ba ni
NG0265:14947: / kha cig gi ni spang bya yin yang */
NG0265:14948: 'dir ye shes chen por mtshon cing nyams chen po yin no //
NG0265:14949: bya byed ma skyes rang bzhin mthong *//
NG0265:14950: de ltar gang gis ston ces na rig pa nyid ma skyes pa las /
NG0265:14951: yul lnga ji ltar shar yang */
NG0265:14952: de nyid bde ba chen po las mi gzhan par
NG0265:14953: mthong la de nyid kyang gnyen pos ma bcos pas
NG0265:14954: rang grol zhing stong par gsal lo //
NG0265:14955: nang gi lnga yang bde chen gyis gzugs la sogs pa ste /
NG0265:14956: bde ba chen po nyid lngar snang la de yang tha mal dang */
NG0265:14958: sgyu ma'i rang bzhin dang stong pa'i cho 'phrul las gzhan ma yin par gsal ba'o //
NG0265:14959: nges par mthong bas ngo bo med //
NG0265:14960: de dag kyang ji ltar mthong zhe na /
NG0265:14961: ji srid du man ngag dang thabs kyi nges pa'i shes rab skyes pa'i tshe /
NG0265:14962: tha dad dang rang rgyud pa'i zhen pa log cing */
NG0265:14963: rig pa'i dkyil 'khor gsal la ma 'dres pa ngo bo stong par mthong ba'o //
NG0265:14964: chu bur sprin dang chu ris ltar //
NG0265:14966: chu dwangs pa la chu bur skyes nas /
NG0265:14967: yang chu nyid du grol ba dang nam mkha' la sprin byung nas de nyid du grol ba dang */
NG0265:14968: chu la rkyen gyis ri mo ji ltar bris kyang
NG0265:14969: chu nyid yin la de yang chur grol ba bzhin
NG0265:14970: no // nges med rang sems dbyings la gtugs //
NG0265:14971: de ltar chos thams cad rig pa nam mkha' ltar mtha' dbus med pa nyid nyon mongs lnga dang */
NG0265:14973: dran rtog gi 'du shes su rang gi sems ji lta bar shes te /
NG0265:14974: de nyid chos dbyings thog mtha' med pa'i ngo bo la gnas shing grol lo //
NG0265:14975: snang ba sems la gang zhugs pas //
NG0265:14976: de bas na ji snyed pa'i snang ba rang bzhin
NG0265:14977: gyis sems nyid ma bcos pa'i thig le la rtogs
NG0265:14978: pa'i nyams kyi ngang du zhugs pas sgo gsum gyis
NG0265:14979: bya btsal med par rig pa gang ltar gsal yang
NG0265:14980: */ 'du shes kun las grol bas de bzhin nyid do //
NG0265:14981: yul sems bden pa'i 'du shes med //
NG0265:14982: de la yul nyid rig par snang ba dang */
NG0265:14983: snang ba nyid sems su 'dus par gsal bas /
NG0265:14984: yul la bden pa'i 'du shes med la /
NG0265:14985: sems la sems kyis bltas pas /
NG0265:14987: mthong ba med par bstan pa dang */
NG0265:14988: sems kyang bden par ma grub cing med de gang
NG0265:14989: du 'du shes dang bya ba zad pa de ni
NG0265:14990: chos nyid ma bcos pa ste /
NG0265:14991: de la ni bsgom mi bsgom gang yang bdag tu med do //
NG0265:14992: dus gsum ma bcos snying po'i sems //
NG0265:14993: gang du lung dang bla ma'i man ngag gis /
NG0265:14994: snang srid byang chub sems nyid ma bcos pa'i bde
NG0265:14995: ba chen por gtan la phebs nas de dag nyid
NG0265:14996: la nges par gnas pa'i tshe /
NG0265:14997: dus gsum du gzung du med pa'i rig pa ma
NG0265:14998: skyes pa la gnyen po dang thabs kyis 'thos su
NG0265:14999: med de snying po byang chub kyi sems su rang
NG0265:15000: gsal ba'o // dngos su bltas pas 'du shes med //
NG0265:15001: de nyid la gnas par bya ba ni /
NG0265:15002: snga phyi spangs pa'i bde ba chen po la gnas pa'i dus su rang rig cing dran pa dang */
NG0265:15003: thun mong dang gzhan dngos la bltas pas kyang */
NG0265:15004: 'du shes kyang med la rang gi ngo bo la
NG0265:15005: bltas kyang 'du shes thams cad las gros bar 'gyur
NG0265:15006: te chu dang nam mkha' bzhin no //
NG0265:15007: snga phyi rtog pa'i ris mi gcad //
NG0265:15008: de la rig pa'i gnas lugs ni snga phyi spangs
NG0265:15009: pa'i bde ba chen po la gnas pa'i dus su
NG0265:15010: dus gsum mnyam pa nyid kyi ngo bo la /
NG0265:15011: rigs snga ma'i rjes mi bcad phyi ma la yid
NG0265:15012: mi 'jug / da ltar rang gi ngo bo la
NG0265:15013: blo mi gnas te rang bzhin gyis gsal ba'o //
NG0265:15014: phyi rol gang mthong yul nyid de //
NG0265:15015: gal te rtog pa chung ngam yun ring nas yul
NG0265:15016: du ston pa byung na gang gi tshe don mi
NG0265:15017: gsal bas shes pa yul lnga la g.yo ba byung
NG0265:15018: ba'i tshe shes pa la gang snang ba de nyid
NG0265:15019: yul nyid do // de nyid brtags pas nang la
NG0265:15020: thug / yul de nyid gang la byung brtags pas
NG0265:15021: yul nyid do // / gzhan las ma byung ste /
NG0265:15022: nang gi sems nyid la thug go //
NG0265:15023: gnyis ka sems nyid dben pa ste //
NG0265:15024: 'o na phyi nang gnyis kar snang ba'i sems de gang yin zhe na /
NG0265:15025: bshad pa'i phyi rol gyi snang ba dang nang rig
NG0265:15026: pa'i snang ba gnyis ka sems nyid kho na yin
NG0265:15027: la / de la ni phyi nang du rgyu ba'i 'du shes kyis dben pa ste /
NG0265:15028: phyogs su zhen pa ma lus pa zad pa'i phyir ro //
NG0265:15029: brtags pas stong pa'i ngang la thim //
NG0265:15030: de'i tshe yul dang shes pa cir snang zhing mthong
NG0265:15031: ba la bltas pas gnyen po med par rang nyid
NG0265:15032: stong ste / phyogs kyi zhen pa zad pa la bya'o //
NG0265:15033: dran rig gang byung bltas pas 'jig / 'o na
NG0265:15034: lta byed kyi rig pa de yod dam zhe na
NG0265:15035: / gang du phyi rol gyi zhen pa ma lus
NG0265:15036: par zad kyang myong ba dang tshor ba dang zhen
NG0265:15037: pa dang yid la byed cing snyam du sems pa
NG0265:15039: de lta bu sna tshogs gang byung yang */
NG0265:15040: ngo bo la bltas pas rang bzhin du 'jig par 'gyur te /
NG0265:15041: de ni rang byung rang zhi'o //
NG0265:15042: de 'dra'i nyams ldan dbang bskur bya //
NG0265:15043: nam mkha' nas yum rnams kyis tshigs su bcad pa'i dbyangs brjod /
NG0265:15044: lha mo rnams kyis mchod pa 'bul byang chub sems dpa' rnams kyis bkra shis brjod /
NG0265:15045: sangs rgyas rnams kyis bum pas dbang bskur bas /
NG0265:15046: ru tra'i rnam shes la gnas pa'i las nyon gyi
NG0265:15047: bag chags ma lus pa dag nas me long lta
NG0265:15048: bu'i ye shes su gyur to //
NG0265:15049: de yang nyon mongs zhe sdang dag / rnam shes kyi phung po gnas 'gyur /
NG0265:15050: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis bag chags bdag
NG0265:15051: gi rgyud la bzhag pas lus mi bskyod pa'i rdul
NG0265:15053: sangs rgyas rnams ni thams cad kyi /
NG0265:15055: gsang gsum gnas las byung ba yi /
NG0265:15056: khams gsum sems can kun gyis phyag byas pa'i //
NG0265:15057: rdo rje'i sems dpa'i bum pa dbang bskur chen po sbyin //
NG0265:15058: sarba ta tha ga ta badzra a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NG0265:15060: sangs rgyas rnams kyis rin po che'i cod pan @#//
NG0265:15061: bdag gi spyi bor bzhag nas dbang bskur bas nyon
NG0265:15062: mongs pa nga rgyal dag / tshor ba'i phung po
NG0265:15064: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis bag chags bdag
NG0265:15065: gi rgyud la bzhag pas rin 'byung gi rdul phra
NG0265:15066: rab kyis bdag gis lus gang bar bsam mo //
NG0265:15067: sangs rgyas rnams ni thams cad kyi /
NG0265:15069: gsang gsum gnas las byung ba yis /
NG0265:15070: khams gsum sems can kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NG0265:15071: rin chen 'byung ldan cod pan gyi dbang bskur chen po khyod la sbyin //
NG0265:15072: sngags kyis bum pa bzhag pa //
NG0265:15073: sarba ta tha ga ta rat+na a b+hi shiny+tsa mam / ! skur mkhan //
NG0265:15074: sangs rgyas kun gyi rdo rje'i dbang */
NG0265:15076: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NG0265:15077: 'di de sangs rgyas thams cad de /
NG0265:15080: shin tu grub phyir rdo rje long *//
NG0265:15081: lag g.yas su rdo rje byin nas dbang bskur bas
NG0265:15082: nyon mongs 'dod chags 'du shes so sor rtog pa
NG0265:15083: ru tra'i rgyud la bzhag pas /
NG0265:15084: lus snang ba mtha' yas kyi rdul phra rab kyis gang ba'o //
NG0265:15085: om badzra a d+hi pa ti s+t+wam badzra sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NG0265:15086: sngags kyis brtan par bya ba /
NG0265:15087: lag pa g.yon pa dril bu byin nas dbang bskur
NG0265:15088: bas nyon mongs pa phrag dog dag bya ba grub
NG0265:15089: pa'i ye shes / 'du byed kyi phung po /
NG0265:15091: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes /
NG0265:15092: ru tra'i rgyud la bzhag pas don grub kyi rdul
NG0265:15093: phra rab kyis lus gang ba'o / ! / 'di
NG0265:15094: ni rdzas gang shes rab dril bu ste //
NG0265:15095: de ring slob ma gang khyod la dbang bskur bas /
NG0265:15097: las kyi rigs su bdag gyur te /
NG0265:15099: chos nyid grub phyir dril bu long *//
NG0265:15100: om badzra sngags kyis byin brlab pa /
NG0265:15101: a ti du ma sa ma ya ham ham /
NG0265:15103: rnam par snang mdzad ston pa yis /
NG0265:15105: khyod la rdo rje'i ming de bzhin gshegs pa thams
NG0265:15106: cad kyi ming gi dbang bskur nas ming btags pas
NG0265:15108: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes /
NG0265:15112: rdo rje'i ming 'di gzung bar bya //
NG0265:15113: om badzra sa twa a b+hi shiny+tsa sngags kyi ming btags pa /
NG0265:15114: mi badzra a b+hi she ka / ga ming btags nas bod pa //
NG0265:15115: kye kye dpal ldan rdo rje che ge mo //
NG0265:15116: hu~m a+om ah lag pa g.yas par rdo rjes dbang
NG0265:15117: bskur bas thabs rdo rje las snying rje ma 'gags
NG0265:15118: par rdzogs par gtang ba ni / ! / 'di
NG0265:15119: de sangs rgyas thams cad de //
NG0265:15120: phyag na rdo rje'i lag na 'dug / rtag par
NG0265:15121: khyod kyis kyang lag pa'i srin lag la rtag tu
NG0265:15122: bcir bzung ste / lag na rdo rje'i brtul shugs dang ldan /
NG0265:15125: om sarba thams cad ta tha ga ta sarba de
NG0265:15126: bzhin gshegs pa thams cad ta tha de bzhin sid+d+hi
NG0265:15127: grub pa badzra rdo rje sa ma ya hu~m /
NG0265:15128: dam tshig ! rdo rje'i de kho na nyid brjod pa //
NG0265:15129: thog mtha' med pa'i sems dpa' ni //
NG0265:15130: rdo rje sems dpa' ni sku gsung thugs 'khor ba'i nyes pa dang bral nas myang 'das kyi /
NG0265:15131: bde ba'i mchog / kun tu bzang po bzang ste
NG0265:15132: dang du mi len ngan te dor ba med pas
NG0265:15133: kun bdag nyid // bcom ldan 'das dpal mchog dang po'i skyes bu la'o //
NG0265:15135: rdo rje chen po / ! lha gang gang bskur //
NG0265:15136: 'di de rnal 'byor ma shes rab dril bu skye ba med par mkhyen pa'o /
NG0265:15140: shes rab dbyangs kyis rjes 'gror bshad /
NG0265:15141: khyod kyis kyang ni lag pa g.yon pa'i srin lag la dril bu /
NG0265:15143: pas sgrib pa bral te nyon mongs lnga dag /
NG0265:15144: byang chub mchog tu ye shes rgyas te mkhyen pa
NG0265:15145: ma lus pa dang ldan rgyal bas bzhed /
NG0265:15146: d+harma d+ha tu chos dbyings skye med a /
NG0265:15147: dril bu'i de nyid brjod pas //
NG0265:15148: srid pa ngo bo nyid kyis dag / srid pa rang gi ngo bo stong pas na //
